15:04.528 --> 15:07.156
UH, YEAH.
BLACK'S FINE. THANKS.

15:07.156 --> 15:10.326
DID SHE TELL YOU ANYTHING ELSE
ABOUT YOUR FATHER'S WILL?

15:10.326 --> 15:11.869
