BE DIVIDED EVENLY

15:25.716 --> 15:27.676
BETWEEN YOURSELF AND DELIA --
50/50.

15:27.676 --> 15:29.136
WHAT KIND OF CREDITORS?

15:29.136 --> 15:31.597
YOUR FATHER HAD A 30-YEAR
MORTGAGE ON THE HOUSE

15:31.597 --> 15:33.515
OF WHICH 10 YEARS WAS LEFT
UNPAID,

15:33.515 --> 15:35.851
AND THE PROPERTY TAXES COME DUE
NEXT MONTH.

15:35.851 --> 15:38.604
