15:57.039 --> 15:58.958
FIRST STEP IS TO SCHEDULE
A CONFERENCE CALL

15:58.958 --> 16:01.251
BETWEEN YOU, ME, AND DELIA TO
PORE OVER THE DETAILS,

16:01.251 --> 16:02.836
