SAME PAGE.

16:02.836 --> 16:04.505
THAT'S FINE, MR. WALKER.

16:04.505 --> 16:08.467
WHEN ALL'S SAID AND DONE, HOW
MUCH TO YOU THINK WE'LL OWE?

16:08.467 --> 16:11.720
