"NUMEROUS CREDITORS."

16:16.016 --> 16:17.518
ON THE NEGATIVE SIDE.

16:17.518 --> 16:20.062
ON THE PLUS SIDE, HE DID
HAVE A COMPLETE PORTFOLIO,

16:20.062 --> 16:22.523
AND THE HOME AND PROPERTY ARE
SUBSTANTIAL ASSETS.

16:22.523 --> 16:23.732
