ESTIMATES

16:27.111 --> 16:29.071
IN CASE UNFORESEEN DEBTS
CROP UP,

16:29.071 --> 16:31.031
BUT CONSERVATIVELY,
AFTER TAXES,

16:31.031 --> 16:33.534
YOU SHOULD COME AWAY WITH
ABOUT $800,000, EACH.

16:35.327 --> 16:37.079
HERE'S A COPY OF THE WILL
FOR YOU.

16:37.079 --> 16:39.581
AND I'LL BE IN TOUCH REGARDING
THE CONFERENCE CALL.

16:39.581 --> 16:41.667
IT WAS NICE TO MEET YOU.

16:41.667 --> 16:43.585
[ Breathless ] YOU TOO.

16:49.633 --> 16:52.261
I'VE BEEN TRYING TO GET
IN TOUCH WITH YOU, MR. LOWE.

16:52.261 --> 16:53.345
WHERE YOU BEEN?

16:53.345 --> 16:54.388
ON THE GOLF COURSE.

16:54.388 --> 16:56.015
