IN WESTCHESTER.

16:58.392 --> 17:00.185
ARE YOU ALWAYS
SO HARD TO FIND?

17:00.185 --> 17:02.730
I WANTED SOME PEACE,
SO I TURNED OFF MY PHONE.

17:02.730 --> 17:05.065
I'D LIKE TO KNOW HOW SCOTT
JUST DISAPPEARED

17:05.065 --> 17:07.276
UNDER MY EX-WIFE'S NOSE.

17:07.276 --> 17:09.278
WHEN'S THE LAST TIME YOU SAW
YOUR SON?
LAST SUNDAY.

17:09.278 --> 17:11.321
CAN YOU ACCOUNT FOR YOUR
WHEREABOUTS

17:11.321 --> 17:13.157
FROM LAST NIGHT
TO THIS MORNING?

17:13.157 --> 17:14.283
WHAT? WHY?

17:14.283 --> 17:16.869
BECAUSE WE NEED TO
RULE YOU OUT AS A SUSPECT.

17:16.869 --> 17:18.037
I DIDN'T TAKE SCOTT.

17:18.037 --> 17:20.372
THEN LET US RULE YOU OUT
AND FIND OUT WHO DID.

17:20.372 --> 17:21.623
WHERE WERE YOU?

17:21.623 --> 17:24.084
I WAS OUT TO DINNER WITH A
FRIEND AND HIS WIFE

17:24.084 --> 17:25.210
FROM 8:00 TO 10:30,

17:25.210 --> 17:27.296
AND THEN I WAS HOME
TILL THIS MORNING.

17:27.296 --> 17:28.630
I GOT PICKED UP AT 6:00.

17:28.630 --> 17:31.050
CAN ANYONE VOUCH FOR YOU FROM
10:30 TO 6:00?

17:31.050 --> 17:32.301
I WAS SLEEPING!

17:32.301 --> 17:34.470
WHICH I DOUBT IS WHAT
CATHERINE WAS DOING

17:34.470 --> 17:36.472
AND PROBABLY WHY
WE'RE IN THIS MESS.

17:36.472 --> 17:38.432
WHAT'S YOUR BEEF
WITH YOUR EX-WIFE?

17:38.432 --> 17:41.143
SHE'S UNTRUSTWORTHY.
HER FOCUS IN LIFE IS PARTYING.

17:41.143 --> 17:42.811
IS THAT WHY
YOU'RE DIVORCED?

17:42.811 --> 17:43.896
YES.

17:43.896 --> 17:45.230
HOW'D SHE GET CUSTODY?

17:45.230 --> 17:47.691
SHE ACCUSED ME OF BEING THE ONE
WHO WAS CHEATING

17:47.691 --> 17:48.942
AND GOING OUT AND, UH...

17:48.942 --> 17:51.236
I BLEW UP IN COURT AND
CALLED HER A BITCH.

17:51.236 --> 17:53.489
WE HAD A FEMALE JUDGE,
AND THAT WAS THAT.

17:53.489 --> 17:55.783
IF HIS MOM'S IRRESPONSIBLE
AND OUT PARTYING,

17:55.783 --> 17:58.494
