TO STAY OUT OF JAIL.

18:04.458 --> 18:07.336
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU TALKING
ABOUT? MY SON IS MISSING.

18:07.336 --> 18:10.047
IF YOU GOT HIM, WE'LL FIND OUT,
AND IT'S SERIOUS.

18:10.047 --> 18:11.965
BUT IF THIS WAS A
MISUNDERSTANDING

18:11.965 --> 18:14.259
AND WE HEAR THAT NOW,
IT CAN ALL GO AWAY.

18:14.259 --> 18:16.470
WE WERE MAKING PROGRESS
IN FAMILY COURT.

18:16.470 --> 18:18.347
I WAS GETTING BETTER
VISITATION.

18:18.347 --> 18:19.765
