18:29.942 --> 18:31.860
ALL I KNOW IS STEVE.
HE'S A DRUNK.

18:31.860 --> 18:33.612
THEY FIGHT ALL THE TIME,

18:33.612 --> 18:35.823
AND HE SMOKES AROUND SCOTT,
AGGRAVATING HIS ASTHMA.

18:35.823 --> 18:37.533
SO THIS STEVE IS AROUND
A LOT?

18:37.533 --> 18:38.826
I THINK HE LIVES THERE.

18:38.826 --> 18:41.036
I KNOW IT'S ENOUGH
FOR SCOTT TO HATE HIM.

18:41.036 --> 18:43.372
SO, WHERE IS CATHERINE?
CAN I SPEAK TO HER?

18:43.372 --> 18:45.040
NO, YOU KEEP CLEAR
OF HER.

18:45.040 --> 18:47.042
ANY DEVELOPMENTS, WE'LL BE IN
TOUCH.

18:47.042 --> 18:48.252
