19:33.964 --> 19:35.132
WHO'S STEVE?

19:35.132 --> 19:36.383
WHAT BROUGHT HIM UP?

19:36.383 --> 19:37.968
YOUR EX-HUSBAND.
WHO IS HE?

19:37.968 --> 19:39.219
HE'S A GUY I'M SEEING.

19:39.219 --> 19:40.804
WHY DIDN'T YOU MENTION HIM
BEFORE?

19:40.804 --> 19:42.222
WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL?

19:42.222 --> 19:44.808
WE ASKED IF ANYBODY ELSE HAD
ACCESS TO THE APARTMENT.

19:44.808 --> 19:46.560
