ON MY MIND.

19:46.560 --> 19:48.395
HOW'S HE GET ALONG
WITH YOUR SON?

19:48.395 --> 19:50.022
FINE. THAT'S NOT WHAT WE HEAR.

19:50.022 --> 19:52.024
FROM WHOM, MY EX?
WHAT DO YOU EXPECT?

19:52.024 --> 19:54.234
