ON RECORD

19:55.903 --> 19:58.780
TO USE AGAINST ME IN FAMILY
COURT TO GET CUSTODY OF SCOTT.

19:58.780 --> 20:00.741
SO SCOTT AND STEVE
ARE BEST BUDDIES?

20:00.741 --> 20:03.327
