SHOULD HAVE TOLD US

20:27.267 --> 20:28.268
THAT YOU DIDN'T?

20:28.268 --> 20:29.561
NO.

20:29.561 --> 20:32.981
IS IT CLEAR TO YOU NOW THAT
IT SLOWS UP FINDING YOUR SON?

20:32.981 --> 20:34.733
YES. I'M SORRY.

20:36.151 --> 20:37.444
I'M SORRY.

20:37.444 --> 20:40.197
STEVE'S LAST NAME?

20:40.197 --> 20:41.573
DANZIG.

20:41.573 --> 20:44.701
WHERE WE CAN FIND HIM.

21:08.517 --> 21:09.851
STEVE DANZIG?

21:09.851 --> 21:10.936
YEAH.

21:10.936 --> 21:12.980
