21:14.523 --> 21:15.524
CATHERINE'S KID?

21:15.524 --> 21:17.109
HE STILL HASN'T TURNED UP?

21:17.109 --> 21:19.111
WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW HIM?

21:19.111 --> 21:20.237
A COUPLE DAYS AGO.

21:20.237 --> 21:22.698
YOU BEEN NEAR THEIR APARTMENT
SINCE THEN?

21:22.698 --> 21:23.907
NO.

21:23.907 --> 21:25.200
YOU DON'T LIVE THERE?

21:25.200 --> 21:27.035
I JUST STAY THERE
SOMETIMES.

21:27.035 --> 21:29.413
WELL, WHY NOT
THE LAST TWO DAYS?

21:29.413 --> 21:31.331
'CAUSE WE'RE COOLING
A LITTLE.

21:31.331 --> 21:32.624
WHY?

21:32.624 --> 21:34.751
WE JUST ARE.
I DON'T KNOW WHERE SCOTT IS.

21:34.751 --> 21:36.962
HOW'D YOU AND SCOTT
GET ALONG?
FINE.

21:36.962 --> 21:39.089
THIS KID'S BEEN MISSING
SINCE LAST NIGHT.

21:39.089 --> 21:40.799
EVERY MINUTE
THAT'S HE'S NOT FOUND

21:40.799 --> 21:42.467
MAKES IT LESS LIKELY
HE'S SAFE,

21:42.467 --> 21:44.219
WHICH MAKES
OUR PATIENCE GET THIN

21:44.219 --> 21:46.138
FOR PEOPLE WHO AREN'T
HONEST WITH US.

21:46.138 --> 21:47.556
HE WASN'T
MY KIND OF KID.

21:47.556 --> 21:49.349
I WASN'T HIS KIND
OF DADDY FIGURE.

21:49.349 --> 21:50.767
I DON'T KNOW WHERE HE IS.

21:50.767 --> 21:53.103
CHECK CONEY ISLAND
OR THE MOVIE THEATERS.

21:53.103 --> 21:54.396
YOU EVER FIGHT WITH HIM?

21:54.396 --> 21:57.024
HE'D YELL THAT I WASN'T SUPPOSED
TO BE AROUND.

21:57.024 --> 21:58.233
I'D IGNORE HIM.

21:58.233 --> 22:00.819
STILL, LIFE WOULD BE EASIER
WITH HIM OUT OF THE WAY.

22:00.819 --> 22:03.196
FORGET IT. I'M NOT TALKING TO
YOU ANYMORE.

22:06.366 --> 22:07.617
YOU GOT A RECORD?

22:07.617 --> 22:09.077
ANSWER US, STEVE.

22:09.077 --> 22:11.955
I GOT TWO ASSAULT COLLARS
FROM YEARS AGO.

22:11.955 --> 22:15.167
AND SINCE THEN, YOU'VE BEEN
IN ANGER MANAGEMENT

22:15.167 --> 22:17.961
AND DOING YOGA --
REALLY MELLOWING OUT.

22:17.961 --> 22:19.629
I QUIT FIGHTING IN BARS,

22:19.629 --> 22:21.757
WHICH IS WHAT THOSE COLLARS
WERE ABOUT --

22:21.757 --> 22:23.133
NOT KIDNAPPING OR WHATEVER.

22:23.133 --> 22:25.552
ACCOUNT FOR YOURSELF
LAST NIGHT.

22:25.552 --> 22:27.262
SNAKEBITE BAR --
8:00 TO 2:00.

22:27.262 --> 22:29.765
WELL, YOU'RE COMING IN
WHILE WE CHECK IT OUT.

22:29.765 --> 22:31.099
I GOTTA GET THAT BIKE OFF.

22:31.099 --> 22:32.559
LET'S GO. COME ON.

22:32.559 --> 22:35.020
CAN I CLOSE MY SHOP?

22:35.020 --> 22:36.355
MAKE IT FAST.

22:40.275 --> 22:43.820
WHEN WE PRINTED OUT ALL THE
FILES IN THIS MAN'S COMPUTER

22:43.820 --> 22:46.615
THAT RELATED
TO ONLINE CHATS AND E-MAILS,

22:46.615 --> 22:49.618
WE FOUND A LOT OF CORRESPONDENCE
WITH YOUR SON.

22:49.618 --> 22:52.496
REGARDING SEX --
IS THAT WHAT YOU'RE SAYING?

22:52.496 --> 22:55.207
IT'S CRYPTIC,
