35:31.087 --> 35:33.673
HAVE YOU EVER HAD SEXUAL URGES
TOWARD CHILDREN?

35:33.673 --> 35:34.799
NO. NO WAY.

35:34.799 --> 35:36.968
YOU'VE NEVER APPROACHED
A MINOR FOR SEX?

35:36.968 --> 35:38.886
NEVER. I'M OFFENDED
THAT YOU'D ASK.

35:38.886 --> 35:40.138
I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS.

35:40.138 --> 35:42.140
I CAN'T BELIEVE
I BOTHERED TO HELP YOU.

35:42.140 --> 35:43.683
WELL, WE DO APPRECIATE IT,

35:43.683 --> 35:46.018
AND WE'D LIKE TO RETURN THE
FAVOR BY HELPING YOU.

35:46.018 --> 35:48.396
SEE, POSSESSING CHILD
PORNOGRAPHY IS A FELONY,

35:48.396 --> 35:50.148
AND IT CAN GET YOU
JAIL TIME,

35:50.148 --> 35:52.358
BUT IF ADMIT YOU HAVE
WRONG FEELINGS TOWARD KIDS,

35:52.358 --> 35:55.027
WE COULD ASK THE D.A. FOR
PROBATION WITH COUNSELING

35:55.027 --> 35:56.279
AS PART OF YOUR SENTENCE.

35:56.279 --> 35:57.697
BUT YOU'VE GOTTA ADMIT IT.

35:57.697 --> 36:01.450
I'VE NEVER TOUCHED A CHILD --
NEVER.

36:01.450 --> 36:03.494
CAN YOU ACCOUNT FOR YOUR
WHEREABOUTS

36:03.494 --> 36:05.746
FROM 8:00 LAST NIGHT
TILL THIS MORNING?

36:05.746 --> 36:07.123
YOU THINK I HAD SOMETHING TO DO
WITH THIS BOY BEING KILLED?

36:07.123 --> 36:08.166
WHERE WERE YOU?

36:08.166 --> 36:10.126
AT MY AUNT'S HOUSE
ALL NIGHT.

36:10.126 --> 36:12.044
WE'LL NEED TO TALK
TO HER.

36:12.044 --> 36:13.504
WELL, FINE.

36:13.504 --> 36:18.467
I'VE NEVER HURT A CHILD
OR TOUCHED A CHILD --

36:18.467 --> 36:20.052
NEVER...EVER.

36:20.052 --> 36:21.971
BUT YOU'VE WANTED TO.

36:24.182 --> 36:27.393
[ SOBS ]

36:27.393 --> 36:28.769
DO YOU WANT OUR HELP?

36:32.064 --> 36:33.316
[ SOBBING ]

36:40.656 --> 36:44.202
SECOND MESSAGE, MS. LAPPIN.
PLEASE CALL AS SOON AS YOU CAN.

36:44.202 --> 36:47.163
NO ANSWER AT HER WORK EITHER.
I LEFT WORD.

36:47.163 --> 36:49.582
HAVE YOU TALKED TO
CATHERINE LOWE?

36:49.582 --> 36:51.167
WHACKED OUT ON VALIUM.

36:51.167 --> 36:53.920
WE'LL GET HER AGAIN
WHEN SHE WAKES UP.

36:53.920 --> 36:55.963
WHAT'D THE GUY SAY
WHO FOUND THE BODY?

36:55.963 --> 36:59.175
UH, CAN PICKER -- SAID HE WENT
IN TO SET UP CAMP FOR THE NIGHT,

36:59.175 --> 37:01.510
SAW LEGS STICKING OUT
FROM UNDER THE BAG.

37:01.510 --> 37:02.595
WASN'T BURIED AT ALL?

37:04.096 --> 37:05.264
ANYTHING ON CANVASS?

37:05.264 --> 37:07.433
NOTHING -- FOUND
A COUPLE OF APARTMENTS

37:07.433 --> 37:10.186
WITH WINDOWS FACING THE VACANT
LOT -- WEREN'T HOME.

37:10.186 --> 37:11.520
HOW ABOUT DANZIG'S ALIBI?

37:11.520 --> 37:13.231
CAN'T FIND THE GIRL.

37:13.231 --> 37:15.650
WE'RE GONNA HEAD BACK OUT
AND RECANVASS THOSE APARTMENTS.

37:15.650 --> 37:17.109
GIVE IT TO NIGHT WATCH.

37:17.109 --> 37:19.403
I WANT EVERYONE TO GO HOME
AND GET SOME REST.

37:19.403 --> 37:21.364
WE'LL GO AT IT
FRESH IN THE MORNING.

37:21.364 --> 37:23.366
[ SIGHS ]

37:23.366 --> 37:26.452
GO.

37:29.121 --> 37:30.248
ANYONE EAT TODAY?

37:30.248 --> 37:31.457
I'M NOT HUNGRY.

37:31.457 --> 37:34.669
WELL, NEITHER AM I, BUT
WE GOTTA CLEAR OUR HEADS.

37:56.315 --> 37:58.859
SO, HOW WAS DISNEY WORLD?

37:58.859 --> 38:00.236
IT WAS FUN.

38:00.236 --> 38:01.904
WELL, THEO LOVED IT.

38:01.904 --> 38:04.365
DID HE HAVE
A FAVORITE RIDE?

38:04.365 --> 38:05.908
THE HAUNTED HOUSE.

38:05.908 --> 38:09.996
HE LIKED THE BEARS, TOO --
THE COUNTRY BEAR JAMBOREE.

38:09.996 --> 38:11.580
WE SAW THAT FIVE TIMES.

38:11.580 --> 38:15.459
EVERY TIME THEY STARTED PLAYING
THEIR LITTLE INSTRUMENTS --

38:15.459 --> 38:18.713
THE WASHBOARD AND JUG --
HIS EYES WOULD LIGHT UP.

38:18.713 --> 38:20.381
I COULDN'T FIGURE IT OUT.

38:20.381 --> 38:21.799
HE WAS REALLY SWEET.

38:26.178 --> 38:27.596
ANYTHING HAPPEN LAST WEEK?

38:27.596 --> 38:29.640
UH, LAUNDROMAT
ON BERRY GOT ROBBED.

38:29.640 --> 38:32.184
PERP DROPPED HIS DRIVER'S
LICENSE RUNNING OUT.

38:32.184 --> 38:33.185
SHARP.

38:33.185 --> 38:34.854
OTHERWISE, PRETTY QUIET.

38:34.854 --> 38:38.190
I SAW A GOOD MOVIE --
A FRENCH MOVIE -- "AMELIE."

38:38.190 --> 38:40.443
OH, YEAH, I HEARD
THAT WAS GOOD.

38:40.443 --> 38:41.777
IT WAS REALLY CUTE.

38:44.447 --> 38:46.240
YOU --
YOU SEE IT TOGETHER?

38:46.240 --> 38:47.450
YEAH.

38:47.450 --> 38:49.327
YOU GUYS BEEN GOING OUT?

38:49.327 --> 38:51.662
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
UH, YEAH.

38:51.662 --> 38:52.997
IT'S BEEN GOOD.

38:52.997 --> 38:54.999
[ CHUCKLES ]
THAT'S GREAT.

38:54.999 --> 38:56.042
SINCE WHEN?

38:56.042 --> 38:57.501
THE FIGHT.

38:57.501 --> 38:59.879
I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN.

39:01.714 --> 39:03.507
HUH.

39:03.507 --> 39:05.009
WHAT?

39:05.009 --> 39:06.802
THESE BALL-BREAKING UNIFORMS
GET WIND OF THIS,

39:06.802 --> 39:08.596
THEY'RE GONNA GO
OUT OF THEIR MINDS.

39:08.596 --> 39:09.930
SCREW 'EM.

39:14.602 --> 39:16.270
I'D BETTER ROLL.

39:16.270 --> 39:17.980
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

39:17.980 --> 39:18.981
YEAH.

39:18.981 --> 39:20.107
STAY AWHILE.

39:20.107 --> 39:21.567
THEO'S WITH THE SITTER.

39:21.567 --> 39:24.320
I GOTTA TURN IN EARLY.
I'LL SEE YOU TOMORROW.

39:24.320 --> 39:26.947
GOOD NIGHT.

39:44.256 --> 39:46.175
DID YOU BRUSH
YOUR TEETH?

39:46.175 --> 39:47.385
YEAH.

39:47.385 --> 39:49.929
LET ME SEE.

39:49.929 --> 39:51.055
GOOD.

39:51.055 --> 39:52.973
ALL RIGHT, ONE STORY.
THEN BEDTIME.

39:52.973 --> 39:55.726
DAD, WHEN IS CONNIE
COMING OVER AGAIN?

39:55.726 --> 39:57.103
I DON'T KNOW. SOON.

39:57.103 --> 39:59.688
WHY ISN'T SHE HERE
ALL THE TIME?

39:59.688 --> 40:01.565
'CAUSE, UH,
SHE DOESN'T LIVE HERE.

40:01.565 --> 40:03.526
SHE'S GOT HER
OWN APARTMENT.

40:03.526 --> 40:06.779
I LIKED IN FLORIDA WHEN
SHE WAS AROUND ALL THE TIME.

40:06.779 --> 40:08.239
WELL, THAT WAS SPECIAL.

40:08.239 --> 40:10.449
THIS IS HOW THINGS ARE
NORMALLY.

40:10.449 --> 40:12.326
I LIKED IT BETTER
THE OTHER WAY.

40:12.326 --> 40:14.870
YEAH, I KNOW. I HEARD YOU
THE FIRST TIME, THEO.

40:14.870 --> 40:16.497
YOU WANT TO HEAR
THIS STORY?

40:16.497 --> 40:17.915
YEAH.

40:17.915 --> 40:20.167
"UP AT LAKE WINNEBAGO..."

40:20.167 --> 40:24.797
NEXT TIME CONNIE COMES OVER,
CAN I CALL HER "MOMMY"?

40:24.797 --> 40:26.799
NO, THEO.
SHE'S NOT YOUR MOMMY.

40:26.799 --> 40:28.175
THAT WOULDN'T BE RIGHT.

40:28.175 --> 40:30.594
SHE'S SORT OF ACTS
LIKE A MOMMY.

40:33.180 --> 40:35.599
DO YOU EVER THINK
OF YOUR REAL MOM AT ALL?

40:35.599 --> 40:37.101
I DON'T REMEMBER HER.

40:37.101 --> 40:39.186
WELL, YOUR REAL MOM
LOVED YOU VERY MUCH,

40:39.186 --> 40:40.646
AND IT WOULDN'T BE RIGHT

40:40.646 --> 40:43.649
TO JUST GO CALLING SOMEONE THE
SAME THING YOU CALLED HER.

40:43.649 --> 40:44.775
ARE YOU MAD?

40:44.775 --> 40:46.527
NO, I'M NOT MAD.

40:46.527 --> 40:49.113
IT'S JUST, YOU CAN'T GO THINKING
IT'S AN EASY THING

40:49.113 --> 40:52.241
TO REPLACE SOMEBODY YOU LOVED
AND WHO LOVED YOU BACK.

40:52.241 --> 40:54.201
YOU JUST CAN'T DO THAT
TO PEOPLE.

40:54.201 --> 40:56.579
OKAY.

40:56.579 --> 40:58.706
THEO, YOU WANT TO HEAR
THE STORY?

40:58.706 --> 41:00.124
I WANT TO GO TO BED.

41:00.124 --> 41:02.835
COME ON, THEO.
COME ON, LET'S READ THIS STORY.

41:02.835 --> 41:04.503
I'M TIRED.

41:25.065 --> 41:27.860
GET ANY SLEEP?

41:27.860 --> 41:28.903
YEAH.

41:28.903 --> 41:32.031
YOU WERE TOSSING AROUND
A LOT.

41:34.241 --> 41:36.994
HOW YOU DOING?

41:36.994 --> 41:38.370
OKAY.

41:38.370 --> 41:41.707
I SHOULD PROBABLY
GET GOING.

41:44.460 --> 41:47.046
HAVING DINNER WITH MY DAD
TONIGHT.

41:47.046 --> 41:49.924
SO YOU GUYS ARE STARTING
TO TALK MORE?

41:49.924 --> 41:53.802
YEAH. LITTLE BY LITTLE
GETTING IT BACK.

41:53.802 --> 41:55.846
HMM.

41:55.846 --> 41:57.723
I'M GLAD.

42:01.519 --> 42:04.313
I WANT HIM TO MEET YOU.

42:06.398 --> 42:09.860
THAT'D BE GREAT.
WHEN?

42:09.860 --> 42:12.071
TONIGHT.

42:12.071 --> 42:15.866
WHY DON'T YOU COME TO DINNER
IF YOU DON'T HAVE ANY PLANS?

42:15.866 --> 42:19.537
YOU SURE, 'CAUSE
THAT'S A STEP.

42:19.537 --> 42:21.580
YEAH.

42:21.580 --> 42:27.211
IT'D MEAN A LOT TO ME --
AND HIM.

42:27.211 --> 42:29.046
THEN I'LL BE THERE.

42:40.849 --> 42:42.268
GOOD MORNING, DETECTIVE.

42:42.268 --> 42:43.894
MORNING.

42:43.894 --> 42:45.896
HEY.

42:45.896 --> 42:47.815
YOU ALL RIGHT?

42:47.815 --> 42:49.900
UH, THEO'S BEEN
CARRYING ON.

42:49.900 --> 42:50.901
ABOUT?

42:50.901 --> 42:52.069
WE GOT A D.O.A. FEMALE

42:52.069 --> 42:54.029
OVER AT HER APARTMENT
ON 28th STREET.

42:54.029 --> 42:56.407
YOU AND CONNIE, LET ME KNOW
IF YOU NEED HELP.

42:56.407 --> 42:58.284
WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH SCOTT LOWE?

42:58.284 --> 42:59.952
WE GOT A CAUSE OF DEATH
YET?

42:59.952 --> 43:01.495
GUNSHOT TO THE CHEST.

43:01.495 --> 43:03.080
ANY INDICATION
HE WAS ABUSED?

43:03.080 --> 43:04.540
WE GOT M.E. WORKING
ON IT.

43:04.540 --> 43:06.875
THE MOM'S BOYFRIEND,
STEVE DANZIG,

43:06.875 --> 43:08.544
I FINALLY GOT AHOLD OF THE
EX-GIRLFRIEND

43:08.544 --> 43:10.296
THAT HE WAS BANGING
THAT NIGHT.

43:10.296 --> 43:12.214
THEIR STORIES
ARE A COUPLE OF HOURS OFF.

43:12.214 --> 43:13.716
JUNIOR'S BRINGING HIM IN.

43:13.716 --> 43:15.134
WE LIKE HIM?

43:15.134 --> 43:17.678
HE'S A DIRTBAG WHO'S ALREADY
LIED ONCE TO US, SO, YEAH.

43:17.678 --> 43:19.138
THIS IS ALL OVER
THE MEDIA.

43:19.138 --> 43:21.265
I DON'T KNOW IF ANYONE'S SEEN
THE PAPERS.

43:21.265 --> 43:22.474
LET ME WORRY ABOUT THAT.

43:22.474 --> 43:24.310
YOU TAKE CARE
OF WHAT YOU GOTTA DO.

43:24.310 --> 43:26.729
ANDY, YOU AND JOHN
INTERVIEW THE BOYFRIEND.

43:26.729 --> 43:29.398
GREG, YOU AND BALDWIN GO BACK
AND TALK TO THE MOM.

43:29.398 --> 43:31.609
I WANT EVERYONE
WE INTERVIEWED YESTERDAY

43:31.609 --> 43:33.902
RE-INTERVIEWED
NOW THAT IT'S A HOMICIDE.

43:33.902 --> 43:35.904
AND GO AS HARD AT THEM
AS NECESSARY.

43:35.904 --> 43:38.073
THIS IS A 12-YEAR-OLD KID
MURDERED HERE.

43:41.535 --> 43:44.955
HAVE A SEAT, STEVE.

43:48.626 --> 43:50.919
WHERE WERE YOU THE NIGHT
SCOTT LOWE WAS KILLED?

43:50.919 --> 43:52.546
DON'T BOTHER WITH
CONDOLENCES.

43:52.546 --> 43:53.631
WHERE WERE YOU?

43:53.631 --> 43:54.882
I ALREADY TOLD YOU.

43:54.882 --> 43:57.009
I WAS WITH MY EX-GIRLFRIEND,
PENNY LAPPIN.

43:57.009 --> 43:58.761
I DIDN'T TELL YOU
TO BEGIN WITH

43:58.761 --> 44:01.263
BECAUSE I DIDN'T WANT IT GETTING
BACK TO CATHERINE.

44:01.263 --> 44:02.848
WHEN DID YOU LEAVE
PENNY'S?

44:02.848 --> 44:05.267
YOU GUYS ARE AMAZING.
2:00 A.M. I TOLD YOU.

44:05.267 --> 44:06.894
PENNY SAID YOU LEFT
AT MIDNIGHT.

44:06.894 --> 44:09.438
DO YOU SEE A WRISTWATCH
HERE?

44:09.438 --> 44:12.066
I WENT OVER, WE DID IT,
I LEFT.

44:12.066 --> 44:13.400
IT WAS LATE.

44:13.400 --> 44:15.653
IF PENNY SAID MIDNIGHT,
OKAY, SO I WAS OFF A LITTLE.

44:15.653 --> 44:18.072
WHEN A GUY LEAVES AN
EX-GIRLFRIEND'S APARTMENT

44:18.072 --> 44:20.908
AFTER BANGING HER, WHEN
HE KNOWS HE SHOULDN'T BE THERE,

44:20.908 --> 44:22.576
YOU KEEP AN EYE
ON THE CLOCK.

44:22.576 --> 44:25.287
THAT'S YOU.
ME, I DON'T CARE.

44:25.287 --> 44:29.667
SO, WHAT'D YOU DO AFTER YOU LEFT
PENNY'S AT MIDNIGHT?

44:29.667 --> 44:32.169
OKAY, I'M GONNA TELL YOU
THIS ONE MORE TIME.

44:32.169 --> 44:34.296
YOU'RE GONNA TELL US
WHATEVER WE ASK,

44:34.296 --> 44:36.131
HOWEVER MANY TIMES WE ASK
IT.

44:36.131 --> 44:38.801
I LEFT PENNY'S,
I WENT TO MY SHOP.

44:38.801 --> 44:41.595
PASSED OUT ON THE COACH
IN THE BACK.

44:41.595 --> 44:43.305
DID YOU HAVE ANY ARGUMENTS
WITH SCOTT

44:43.305 --> 44:44.932
WHEN YOU WERE LIVING
WITH HIS MOM?

44:44.932 --> 44:47.226
NO.

44:47.226 --> 44:50.562
I KNOW YOU GUYS WANT TO PIN
SCOTT'S DEATH ON ME, BUT, SORRY,

44:50.562 --> 44:53.065
LOOKS LIKE YOU'RE ACTUALLY GONNA
HAVE TO DO SOME WORK

44:53.065 --> 44:54.775
AND FIND OUT WHO DID.

44:54.775 --> 44:57.736
AM I UNDER ARREST OR NOT?
'CAUSE I GOT SOME WORK TO DO.

44:57.736 --> 44:59.238
YEAH, GO TO WORK.

44:59.238 --> 45:02.241
DON'T LET YOUR GIRLFRIEND'S KID
GETTING KILLED RUIN YOUR DAY.

45:02.241 --> 45:04.201
IS THAT WHAT YOU
WANT ME TO DO?

45:04.201 --> 45:06.245
DO YOU WANT ME TO CRY
AND CARRY ON

45:06.245 --> 45:07.830
TO PROVE I DIDN'T DO IT?

45:07.830 --> 45:10.624
WELL, I GOT FEELINGS
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED TO SCOTT,

45:10.624 --> 45:13.919
BUT I'M NOT GONNA BREAK DOWN
TO MAKE YOU GUYS FEEL BETTER.

45:13.919 --> 45:15.254
STAY REACHABLE, STEVE.

45:15.254 --> 45:17.256
YOU LISTEN TO ME.
HEY, I TOLD YOU --

45:17.256 --> 45:18.716
SHUT UP AND LISTEN TO ME.

45:18.716 --> 45:21.218
OR I'LL BE TALKING TO YOU WITH
MY SHOE PRESSED IN YOUR THROAT.

45:21.218 --> 45:24.012
IF YOU HAD SOMETHING TO DO WITH
SCOTT LOWE GETTING KILLED --

45:24.012 --> 45:26.098
YOU GUYS ARE AMAZING.
SHUT UP!

45:26.098 --> 45:29.309
IF THIS WAS AN ACCIDENT,
NOW'S THE TIME TO TELL US.

45:29.309 --> 45:32.354
IF WE GOTTA PROVE IT,
I DON'T CARE WHAT HAPPENED,

45:32.354 --> 45:34.648
I'LL MAKE SURE
YOU GET THE NEEDLE.

45:34.648 --> 45:35.941
AYE, AYE, CAPTAIN.

45:37.067 --> 45:39.069
YOU GET OUT OF HERE.

45:58.964 --> 46:00.090
WHAT DO WE GOT?

46:00.090 --> 46:01.925
ELDERLY WOMAN --
VANESSA GAVIOLA.

46:01.925 --> 46:03.051
HER APARTMENT.

46:03.051 --> 46:04.261
WHO CALLED IT IN?

46:04.261 --> 46:06.263
LARRY TYLER --
LIVES TWO DOORS DOWN.

46:06.263 --> 46:07.598
HE'D DO ODD JOBS FOR HER.

46:07.598 --> 46:10.100
WENT TO CHECK ON HER,
AND THIS IS WHAT HE FOUND.

46:10.100 --> 46:12.227
THIS GUY'S A --
HE'S AN EX-CON.

46:12.227 --> 46:14.354
DID 10 YEARS FOR A RAPE
ASSAULT.

46:14.354 --> 46:17.274
GUESS WE'LL HAVE A
CONVERSATION WITH HIM, THEN.

46:17.274 --> 46:20.444
HE CAME RIGHT OUT WITH IT.
HE WAS BEING HONEST.

46:20.444 --> 46:21.570
ALL RIGHT.

46:21.570 --> 46:23.530
BUILDING SUPER'S
OVER THERE, TOO.

46:23.530 --> 46:25.866
BLACK GUY ON THE STAIRS --
DON GOLDAMMER.

46:25.866 --> 46:27.159
THEY WERE BOTH GOING ON

46:27.159 --> 46:29.578
ABOUT THE OLD LADY'S GRANDSON
AS A SUSPECT.

46:29.578 --> 46:30.996
I DIDN'T GET ANY DETAILS.

46:30.996 --> 46:32.247
KEEP THEM BOTH AROUND.

46:32.247 --> 46:33.332
YOU GOT IT.

46:35.667 --> 46:37.085
[ SIGHS ]

46:39.797 --> 46:42.132
HMM. STRANGLED.

46:42.132 --> 46:43.967
DOESN'T LOOK
LIKE A ROBBERY.

46:43.967 --> 46:46.303
SHE'S GOT AN EX-CON RAPIST
DOING ERRANDS FOR HER.

46:46.303 --> 46:48.388
YEAH, SOMETHING'S
A LITTLE OFF WITH THAT.

46:48.388 --> 46:49.640
I'LL TAKE HIM.

46:49.640 --> 46:51.225
WHY DON'T YOU TALK
TO THE SUPER?

46:51.225 --> 46:52.226
OKAY.

46:55.938 --> 46:57.523
LARRY TYLER?
YEAH.

46:57.523 --> 46:59.066
DETECTIVE McDOWELL.

46:59.066 --> 47:01.109
THAT'S HOW YOU FOUND HER?

47:01.109 --> 47:02.236
YEAH.

47:02.236 --> 47:03.445
DO YOU HAVE A KEY?

47:03.445 --> 47:05.489
NO, THE DOOR WAS
OPEN A LITTLE,

47:05.489 --> 47:08.075
WHICH IS UNUSUAL, SO I
DUCKED MY HEAD IN.

47:08.075 --> 47:10.869
AS I TOLD YOUR OFFICER,
I GOT A RECORD.

47:10.869 --> 47:13.664
I'M NOT TRYING
TO HIDE IT FROM ANYBODY.

47:13.664 --> 47:14.832
RAPE ASSAULT?

47:14.832 --> 47:15.874
YEAH.

47:15.874 --> 47:17.376
AND MRS. GAVIOLA KNEW THAT?

47:17.376 --> 47:18.710
EVERYBODY DID.

47:18.710 --> 47:20.921
WHAT'S THIS ABOUT HER
GRANDSON?

47:20.921 --> 47:23.924
JERRY GAVIOLA.
HE'S A REAL SAD CASE -- JUNKIE.

47:23.924 --> 47:25.342
YOU LIKE HIM FOR DOING THIS?

47:25.342 --> 47:27.761
HE WAS ALWAYS WORKING MRS.
GAVIOLA FOR MONEY.

47:27.761 --> 47:29.429
SHE COULDN'T SAY "NO" TO
HIM.

47:29.429 --> 47:30.597
WE'LL TALK TO HIM,

47:30.597 --> 47:32.850
AND WE'RE GONNA NEED
TO TALK TO YOU.

47:32.850 --> 47:34.101
SURE. I KNOW.

47:36.770 --> 47:38.480
HOW LONG HAS
MRS. GAVIOLA LIVED HERE?

47:38.480 --> 47:39.982
20 YEARS.

47:39.982 --> 47:42.067
DO YOU KNOW
THIS GUY -- LARRY TYLER?

47:42.067 --> 47:44.570
YEAH, I KNOW LARRY.
EVERYBODY HERE DOES.

47:44.570 --> 47:46.238
HOW LONG HAS HE LIVED HERE?

47:46.238 --> 47:47.322
TWO YEARS.

47:47.322 --> 47:48.699
WHAT'S YOUR TAKE ON HIM?

47:48.699 --> 47:51.285
YOU'D NEVER KNOW
HE WAS AN EX-CON.

47:51.285 --> 47:53.203
COURTEOUS,
HELPFUL, HONEST.

47:53.203 --> 47:54.621
LIKE A BOY SCOUT.

47:54.621 --> 47:56.331
I'M TELLING YOU, HE'S A
GOOD GUY.

47:56.331 --> 47:58.792
I TRUST HIM WITH MY
GRANDKIDS.

48:06.008 --> 48:09.845
Baldwin: AND, MS. LOWE,
WE'RE VERY SORRY FOR YOUR LOSS.

48:09.845 --> 48:12.431
FIND WHO KILLED MY SON...
PLEASE.

48:12.431 --> 48:14.600
WE'RE GONNA DO EVERYTHING
WE CAN.

48:14.600 --> 48:15.809
[ SIGHS ]

48:15.809 --> 48:17.811
UH, HAVING GIVEN IT
MORE THOUGHT,

48:17.811 --> 48:19.897
IS THERE ANYONE
YOU'RE LEAVING OUT

48:19.897 --> 48:22.608
WHO COULD HAVE HAD SOMETHING TO
DO WITH YOUR SON'S DEATH?

48:22.608 --> 48:24.067
MY EX-HUSBAND, JIM --

48:24.067 --> 48:26.069
THAT'S THE ONLY PERSON I CAN
THINK ABOUT.

48:26.069 --> 48:28.864
YOU FEEL YOUR EX-HUSBAND WAS
CAPABLE OF KILLING SCOTT?

48:28.864 --> 48:31.116
HE COULD HAVE TAKEN SCOTT,
KIDNAPPED HIM.

48:31.116 --> 48:32.326
I KNOW THAT FOR SURE.

48:32.326 --> 48:34.536
MAYBE SOMETHING WENT WRONG.
I DON'T KNOW.

48:34.536 --> 48:36.830
ARE THERE MEN WHO
HAD ACCESS TO THIS APARTMENT,

48:36.830 --> 48:38.540
OTHER THAN
YOUR BOYFRIEND STEVE?

48:38.540 --> 48:39.958
NO.

48:39.958 --> 48:41.960
NO ONE ELSE HAD KEYS
TO THE APARTMENT?

48:41.960 --> 48:43.337
[ SOBS ]

48:43.337 --> 48:47.591
SCOTT'S BIRTHDAY
IS NEXT WEEK.

48:47.591 --> 48:50.135
HE WAS GONNA BE 13.

48:52.179 --> 48:54.765
I HAD A PARTY PLANNED.

48:54.765 --> 48:56.642
ANYONE ELSE HAVE KEYS,
MA'AM?

48:56.642 --> 48:58.143
NO.

48:58.143 --> 49:00.520
MS. LOWE, YOU SAID
THAT YOU WERE

49:00.520 --> 49:02.898
AT O'DELL'S BAR TWO
NIGHTS AGO.

49:02.898 --> 49:04.691
YEAH.

49:04.691 --> 49:06.276
AND YOU LEFT AT 2:00 A.M.?

49:06.276 --> 49:07.861
YES.

49:07.861 --> 49:09.905
AND YOU WERE AT O'DELL'S THE
WHOLE TIME?

49:09.905 --> 49:11.698
DIDN'T GO ANYWHERE ELSE?

49:11.698 --> 49:14.868
OKAY, I WANT TO BE
VERY CLEAR ABOUT THIS.

49:14.868 --> 49:16.370
IF YOU CAME HERE TO ASK ME

49:16.370 --> 49:18.622
IF I KNOW WHO
COULD HAVE KILLED SCOTT,

49:18.622 --> 49:19.957
FINE, I TOLD YOU.

49:19.957 --> 49:22.876
BUT IF THIS CONVERSATION'S
GONNA TURN AROUND

49:22.876 --> 49:25.963
TO YOU ASKING ME IF
I HAD ANYTHING TO DO WITH,

49:25.963 --> 49:29.257
OR KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT,
MY SON'S DEATH,

49:29.257 --> 49:30.884
YOU STOP RIGHT NOW,

49:30.884 --> 49:33.553
BECAUSE THERE IS ONLY SO MUCH I
CAN TAKE!

49:33.553 --> 49:36.556
WE NEED TO ASK EVERYONE
WHO WAS CLOSE TO SCOTT --

49:36.556 --> 49:37.933
DID YOU HEAR ME?!

49:37.933 --> 49:39.142
CRIME SCENE'S HERE.

49:39.142 --> 49:40.268
YEAH, ONE MINUTE.

49:40.268 --> 49:41.478
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

49:41.478 --> 49:44.147
WE NEED TO PROCESS THE APARTMENT
FOR ANY FINGERPRINTS,

49:44.147 --> 49:46.817
IN CASE THIS WAS AN ABDUCTION.
IT'LL TAKE A FEW HOURS.

49:46.817 --> 49:48.735
IS THERE SOMEONE
YOU CAN STAY WITH --

49:48.735 --> 49:51.321
A FRIEND OR A RELATIVE --
UNTIL CRIME SCENE IS DONE?

49:51.321 --> 49:54.074
YOU'RE KICKING ME OUT
OF MY OWN HOUSE?

49:54.074 --> 49:57.244
THIS HAS TO HAPPEN, MA'AM.

49:57.244 --> 50:00.080
HEY, CATH, WAIT UP.

50:07.671 --> 50:10.173
HAVE A SEAT.

50:12.801 --> 50:14.302
YOU GOT A JOB, LARRY?

50:14.302 --> 50:17.264
YES, I HANG SHEETROCK
FOR DICKERSON CONSTRUCTION.

50:17.264 --> 50:19.307
BEEN DOING IT FOR TWO
YEARS NOW.

50:19.307 --> 50:21.601
IS THAT WHERE YOU WERE
THIS MORNING?

50:21.601 --> 50:23.603
NO, WE'RE BETWEEN JOBS.

50:23.603 --> 50:25.522
WHERE WERE YOU?

50:25.522 --> 50:27.149
MY APARTMENT, READING.

50:27.149 --> 50:29.818
WHAT WAS YOUR RELATIONSHIP LIKE
WITH MRS. GAVIOLA?

50:29.818 --> 50:31.278
I CONSIDERED HER A FRIEND.

50:31.278 --> 50:33.447
I CAN SAY SHE FELT
THE SAME WAY ABOUT ME.

50:33.447 --> 50:35.532
HOW OFTEN DID YOU DO
ODD JOBS FOR HER?

50:35.532 --> 50:37.284
A LOT. SHE COULDN'T
GET AROUND MUCH.

50:37.284 --> 50:38.535
WHAT KIND OF JOBS?

50:38.535 --> 50:40.370
MRS. GAVIOLA HAD
NO FAMILY HERE,

50:40.370 --> 50:42.039
OTHER THAN
HER GRANDSON JERRY,

50:42.039 --> 50:44.541
WHO, LIKE I SAID, WAS A
REAL HEARTACHE FOR HER.

50:44.541 --> 50:45.876
HE COULDN'T KICK DRUGS.

50:45.876 --> 50:48.003
HE'S ALWAYS BE
WORKING HER FOR MONEY.

50:48.003 --> 50:50.130
WE'LL GET ALL THAT
WHEN WE TALK TO JERRY.

50:50.130 --> 50:52.174
WHAT KIND OF JOBS DID YOU DO
FOR HER?

50:52.174 --> 50:55.343
I'D GET GROCERIES FOR HER,
BRING HER MAIL.

50:55.343 --> 50:57.971
I'D COOK FOR HER.
I LIKE TO COOK.

50:57.971 --> 51:00.724
A LOT OF TIME, WE'D JUST
SIT AROUND AND TALK.

51:00.724 --> 51:02.934
SHE GREW UP
DURING THE DEPRESSION,

51:02.934 --> 51:04.936
SO SHE ALWAYS HAD
SOME STORIES.

51:04.936 --> 51:06.271
[ SIGHS ]

51:06.271 --> 51:07.814
YOU STILL ON PAROLE?

51:07.814 --> 51:09.357
TWO MORE YEARS, YEAH.

51:09.357 --> 51:11.651
WE'RE GONNA NEED YOU
TO ACCOUNT FOR YOUR DAY

51:11.651 --> 51:12.819
AND VERIFY EMPLOYMENT.

51:12.819 --> 51:14.821
WE'RE GONNA NEED
TO TALK TO YOUR P.O.

51:14.821 --> 51:16.948
I KNOW WHY YOU'RE TALKING
TO ME RIGHT NOW.

51:16.948 --> 51:18.658
I GOT NO HARD FEELINGS
ABOUT IT.

51:18.658 --> 51:21.203
GOOD.

51:23.663 --> 51:24.873
ANYTHING ON THE MOM?

51:24.873 --> 51:27.209
NO, WE'RE GONNA GO
BY THE BAR SHE WAS AT

51:27.209 --> 51:30.170
THE NIGHT HER SON WENT MISSING,
VERIFY SHE WAS THERE.

51:30.170 --> 51:32.047
CRIME SCENE'S PROCESSING THE
APARTMENT.

51:32.047 --> 51:33.173
Tony: ALL RIGHT.

51:33.173 --> 51:34.800
HEY, I RAN THE DAD'S RECORD.

51:34.800 --> 51:37.761
TOOK A LOITERING COLLAR
IN THE MEATPACKING DISTRICT

51:37.761 --> 51:38.929
15 YEARS AGO.

51:38.929 --> 51:40.847
HE SURE DID.

51:40.847 --> 51:42.057
ARE WE BRINGING HIM IN?

51:42.057 --> 51:43.558
YEAH, HE'S ON HIS WAY.

51:45.477 --> 51:48.063
LOOKING FOR DETECTIVE
SIPOWICZ.

51:48.063 --> 51:49.147
RIGHT HERE.

51:49.147 --> 51:51.817
DETECTIVE GEOGHAN, BOROUGH
TRUSTEE.

51:51.817 --> 51:53.860
YEAH, WE WERE GONNA DO THIS
NEXT WEEK.

51:53.860 --> 51:57.114
I HAD A MEETING HERE,
SO I THOUGHT I'D TRY YOU.

51:57.114 --> 51:58.365
GOT YOUR FOLDER.

51:58.365 --> 52:00.158
ALL RIGHT, REAL QUICK.

52:00.158 --> 52:02.410
JOHN, THERE'S GONNA BE
SOMEONE DROPPING BY

52:02.410 --> 52:03.829
TO PICK UP OUR TIME RECORDS.

52:03.829 --> 52:04.955
HAVE THEM READY.

52:04.955 --> 52:05.997
CERTAINLY.

52:05.997 --> 52:07.541
SIT DOWN.

52:07.541 --> 52:08.667
OKAY.

52:08.667 --> 52:10.877
WANT SOME COFFEE
OR ANYTHING?

52:10.877 --> 52:12.420
I'M GOOD.

52:12.420 --> 52:14.297
IT'S JUST THAT, UH,

52:14.297 --> 52:17.843
A FRIEND OF MINE'S DAD
DIED RECENTLY,

52:17.843 --> 52:20.470
AND I GUESS HE LEFT A MESS
IN TERMS OF PAPERWORK,

52:20.470 --> 52:23.431
SO I WANTED TO MAKE SURE
I WAS UP TO SPEED WITH ALL THAT.

52:23.431 --> 52:25.600
ANYTHING YOU WANT TO KNOW
IN PARTICULAR?

52:25.600 --> 52:27.978
YEAH, MOSTLY IF SOMETHING
HAPPENED TO ME,

52:27.978 --> 52:29.813
WHAT I GOT COMING
FOR MY SON.

52:29.813 --> 52:31.231
HE'S 6.

52:31.231 --> 52:33.608
WELL, TO START, CITY PAYS
A BENEFICIARY

52:33.608 --> 52:36.778
YOUR SALARY, TAX-FREE,
FOR THE REMAINDER OF THEIR LIFE.

52:36.778 --> 52:38.822
IT IT'S A MINOR, TILL
THEY'RE 18.

52:38.822 --> 52:40.407
23, IF THEY GO TO COLLEGE.

52:40.407 --> 52:42.200
YOU ALSO GOT $100,000 COMING

52:42.200 --> 52:44.578
FROM YOUR D.E.A.
INSURANCE POLICY,

52:44.578 --> 52:46.246
PLUS 10 GRAND FOR THE BURIAL.

52:46.246 --> 52:48.248
HE'D BE TAKEN CARE OF?
MM-HMM.

52:48.248 --> 52:51.001
HE'D ALSO GET $10,000
FROM THE POLICE RELIEF FUND.

52:51.001 --> 52:52.127
YOU'RE FIRST GRADE?

52:52.127 --> 52:53.378
YEAH.

52:53.378 --> 52:55.297
YOU KNOW THAT THREE BUCKS
IN CHANGE

52:55.297 --> 52:57.799
YOU PUT IN EVERY DAY FOR THE
D.E.A. ANNUITY BENEFIT?

52:57.799 --> 53:00.010
THAT WOULD PROBABLY PAY OUT
30 OR 40 GRAND.

53:00.010 --> 53:02.387
IS THIS IF I DIE
IN THE LINE OF DUTY OR NOT?

53:02.387 --> 53:05.307
NO, YOU GET HIT BY A BUS
ON THE WAY HOME

53:05.307 --> 53:07.809
OR DROP DEAD
FROM A HEART ATTACK,

53:07.809 --> 53:09.853
THAT'S CALLED A DEATH GAMBLE.

53:09.853 --> 53:11.188
YEAH, HUH?

53:11.188 --> 53:13.231
ANY MONEY DUE YOU FROM
THE CITY IS PRORATED.

53:13.231 --> 53:15.692
LIKE, YOU RETIRED
THE DAY BEFORE YOU DIED.

53:15.692 --> 53:17.068
YOU DIED TODAY,

53:17.068 --> 53:19.529
PROBABLY COME TO ANYWHERE FROM
600 TO 800 GRAND,

53:19.529 --> 53:21.448
PLUS THE $100,000
FROM THE D.E.A.

53:21.448 --> 53:22.782
AND $10,000 FOR BURIAL.

53:22.782 --> 53:25.202
SO EITHER WAY,
MY SON WOULD BE TAKEN CARE OF?

53:25.202 --> 53:26.703
MM-HMM.

53:26.703 --> 53:29.414
CITY AND LIFE INSURANCE
BOTH LIST AS SOLE BENEFICIARY

53:29.414 --> 53:30.749
YOUR WIFE, SYLVIA COSTAS.

53:30.749 --> 53:31.958
THAT STILL WORK?

53:31.958 --> 53:33.084
NO.

53:33.084 --> 53:36.296
NO, SHE PASSED AWAY
THREE YEARS AGO.

53:36.296 --> 53:37.631
SORRY TO HEAR THAT.

53:37.631 --> 53:40.467
ACTUALLY HAPPENS
MORE OFTEN THAN YOU'D THINK --

53:40.467 --> 53:43.094
GUYS NOT UPDATING
THEIR POLICY

53:43.094 --> 53:45.096
AFTER A DIVORCE OR DEATH.

53:45.096 --> 53:48.350
SO I GUESS YOU'D WANT YOUR SON
LISTED AS BENEFICIARY.

53:48.350 --> 53:49.559
YEAH.

53:49.559 --> 53:50.936
FILL THIS OUT.

53:50.936 --> 53:52.187
WITH A MINOR BENEFICIARY,

53:52.187 --> 53:54.105
YOU'RE GONNA WANT TO SET
UP A TRUST.

53:54.105 --> 53:56.900
WHO'S GONNA BE THE GUARDIAN
OF YOUR SON IN CASE YOU DIE?

53:56.900 --> 53:58.944
I'M GONNA HAVE TO DO THIS
SOME OTHER TIME.

53:58.944 --> 54:01.112
SURE.

54:18.129 --> 54:21.132
WE'RE VERY SORRY
FOR WHAT HAPPENED TO SCOTT.

54:21.132 --> 54:23.343
I KEPT HOPING. I KEPT
HOPING.

54:23.343 --> 54:26.554
ANY LEADS, ANY HUNCHES,
ANYTHING?

54:26.554 --> 54:28.473
IT'S VERY EARLY
IN THE INVESTIGATION.

54:28.473 --> 54:30.767
THIS IS GONNA COME BACK TO
SOME SCUMBAG

54:30.767 --> 54:32.727
THAT WAS MIXED UP WITH
CATHERINE.

54:32.727 --> 54:34.145
MR. LOWE, AS INVESTIGATORS,

54:34.145 --> 54:36.398
WE HAVE TO MAINTAIN
COMPLETE OBJECTIVITY.

54:36.398 --> 54:37.857
WE HAVE TO LOOK AT EVERYONE,

54:37.857 --> 54:39.943
AND WE HAVE TO ASK
DIFFICULT QUESTIONS.

54:39.943 --> 54:40.944
I UNDERSTAND.

54:40.944 --> 54:42.946
YOU WERE ARRESTED
FOR LOITERING

54:42.946 --> 54:45.532
IN THE MEATPACKING DISTRICT
15 YEARS AGO.

54:45.532 --> 54:46.700
I REMEMBER, YEAH.

54:46.700 --> 54:47.951
WHAT WAS THAT ALL ABOUT?

54:47.951 --> 54:49.119
WHY?

54:49.119 --> 54:51.162
WE GOTTA ASK SOME
DIFFICULT QUESTIONS.

54:51.162 --> 54:53.456
I HAD AN OPEN BEER
IN THE STREET.

54:53.456 --> 54:55.583
THIS IS WHEN
I WAS IN COLLEGE.

54:55.583 --> 54:56.710
I WAS BEING STUPID.

54:56.710 --> 54:58.211
THIS IS OUTSIDE A GAY CLUB.

54:58.211 --> 54:59.462
I WAS IN FROM UPSTATE.

54:59.462 --> 55:01.464
I'D NEVER SEEN
PEOPLE LIKE THAT.

55:01.464 --> 55:02.632
I WAS DRUNK.

55:02.632 --> 55:04.384
I WENT DOWN THERE TO
RUBBERNECK,

55:04.384 --> 55:05.468
AND I GOT ARRESTED.

55:05.468 --> 55:07.262
IT WAS A COMPLETE
MISUNDERSTANDING.

55:07.262 --> 55:09.597
WE RUN YOUR NAME
FOR PRIOR ARRESTS NATIONWIDE,

55:09.597 --> 55:11.975
ARE WE GONNA FIND
ANY OTHER MISUNDERSTANDINGS?

55:11.975 --> 55:12.976
NO!

55:12.976 --> 55:14.269
WHEN WE ASK PEOPLE,

55:14.269 --> 55:16.396
ARE WE GONNA HEAR
ABOUT A GAY LIFESTYLE?

55:16.396 --> 55:17.731
NO!

55:17.731 --> 55:20.191
THESE MISUNDERSTANDINGS
CONTRIBUTE TO YOUR DIVORCE?

55:20.191 --> 55:23.069
I'M HOPING YOU'RE NOT GOING
WHERE I THINK YOU'RE GOING!

55:23.069 --> 55:25.322
GETTING ANGRY
WILL ONLY MAKE THINGS WORSE,

55:25.322 --> 55:27.699
SO STAY CALM,
UNDERSTAND WHY WE HAVE TO ASK,

55:27.699 --> 55:29.034
AND ANSWER THE QUESTIONS.

55:29.034 --> 55:31.619
I AM NOT GAY! I'M NOT
ATTRACTED TO BOYS!

55:31.619 --> 55:34.664
I WASN'T ATTRACTED TO MY SON!
CAN WE DROP THAT?!

55:34.664 --> 55:37.834
MR. LOWE, DID YOU HAVE ANYTHING
TO DO WITH YOUR SON'S DEATH?

55:37.834 --> 55:38.835
NO!

55:38.835 --> 55:40.879
WE CAN HELP YOU NOW IF YOU
DID.

55:40.879 --> 55:42.422
IF YOU WAIT TILL LATER,

55:42.422 --> 55:45.175
THAT DECISION CAN ADD
10, 20 YEARS IN JAIL.

55:45.175 --> 55:47.010
NOW IS THE TIME
TO TALK TO US

55:47.010 --> 55:48.887
IF YOU HAD ANY INVOLVEMENT
WHATSOEVER.

55:48.887 --> 55:50.305
NO, I DIDN'T!

55:50.305 --> 55:52.766
I WOULD LIKE TO GO NOW
SO YOU CAN DEVOTE YOUR TIME

55:52.766 --> 55:54.392
TO FINDING OUT
WHO KILLED MY SON!

55:54.392 --> 55:55.894
WE'RE GONNA NEED YOU

55:55.894 --> 55:58.646
TO ACCOUNT FOR WHERE YOU WERE
THE DAY SCOTT WAS MURDERED.

56:00.815 --> 56:02.567
I AM DEEPLY OFFENDED.

56:02.567 --> 56:03.818
WE UNDERSTAND.

56:03.818 --> 56:05.695
WRITE DOWN WHERE YOU WERE
TWO DAYS AGO.

56:15.038 --> 56:16.331
DAVE McCLANAHAN?

56:16.331 --> 56:17.791
YEAH.

56:17.791 --> 56:20.335
DETECTIVES JONES AND MEDAVOY.
WE SPOKE ON THE PHONE.

56:20.335 --> 56:21.753
WHAT'S UP?

56:21.753 --> 56:23.129
YOU KNOW A CATHERINE LOWE?

56:23.129 --> 56:25.590
SHE'S A REGULAR. IS THIS
ABOUT HER KID?

56:25.590 --> 56:27.342
WAS SHE IN HERE
ON WEDNESDAY NIGHT?

56:27.342 --> 56:28.426
YEAH.

56:28.426 --> 56:29.969
WHEN SHE LEAVE?

56:29.969 --> 56:32.764
CATHERINE HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH HER KID GETTING KILLED.

56:32.764 --> 56:34.391
WHEN SHE LEAVE?

56:34.391 --> 56:36.643
LATE, LIKE MIDNIGHT.
I DON'T KNOW. I WAS BUSY.

56:36.643 --> 56:38.186
WAS SHE WITH ANY GUYS?

56:38.186 --> 56:39.771
SHE WAS SOCIALIZING.

56:39.771 --> 56:41.022
SHE LEAVE WITH ANYBODY?

56:41.022 --> 56:42.399
NOT THAT I SAW.

56:42.399 --> 56:44.943
ARE YOU GUYS LOOKING AT
CATHERINE FOR DOING THIS?

56:44.943 --> 56:47.404
DAVE, WE GOT PLACES TO BE.
HOW ABOUT ANSWERING?

56:47.404 --> 56:50.365
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT HER
AND ANY GUYS.

56:50.365 --> 56:51.783
THANKS FOR YOUR HELP.

56:54.536 --> 56:56.162
HEY, HEY, ARE YOU GUYS COPS?

56:56.162 --> 56:57.956
YEAH, WHY?

56:57.956 --> 57:00.500
YOU'RE ASKING ABOUT CATHERINE'S
SON, SCOTT, GETTING KILLED?

57:00.500 --> 57:01.876
YOU KNOW ANYTHING?

57:01.876 --> 57:04.087
CATHERINE'S SO
HEAD-OVER-HEELS WITH STEVE,

57:04.087 --> 57:05.463
SHE'S NOT THINKING STRAIGHT.

57:05.463 --> 57:06.840
STEVE, HER BOYFRIEND?

57:06.840 --> 57:10.051
CATH COMES IN UPSET BECAUSE
HER AND STEVE BROKE UP.

57:10.051 --> 57:12.053
WHAT CAUSED IT WAS
STEVE AND SCOTT

57:12.053 --> 57:14.848
GET IN THIS ARGUMENT,
AND STEVE SMACKS SCOTT AROUND.

57:14.848 --> 57:16.516
CATH DIDN'T WANNA TELL
THE COPS

57:16.516 --> 57:18.935
BECAUSE SHE FIGURED IT WOULD
MAKE STEVE LOOK BAD.

57:18.935 --> 57:20.437
AND SHE SWEARS

57:20.437 --> 57:22.730
HE HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH
SCOTT BEING MISSING.

57:22.730 --> 57:26.734
AND NOW SCOTT IS DEAD, SO I
DON'T KNOW.

57:26.734 --> 57:29.070
WHAT'S YOUR NAME, MA'AM?

57:29.070 --> 57:31.698
PAM GALLAHER. I THOUGHT
YOU SHOULD KNOW.

57:31.698 --> 57:33.533
THANKS FOR YOUR HELP, MA'AM.

57:33.533 --> 57:34.742
YEAH.

57:41.583 --> 57:44.252
HAVE A SEAT, JERRY.

57:44.252 --> 57:46.629
WHERE YOU BEEN
THIS MORNING?

57:48.965 --> 57:50.175
WHY?

57:50.175 --> 57:51.634
JUST ANSWER THE QUESTION.

57:51.634 --> 57:54.345
I GOT A BUST CARD FROM THE ACLU
IN MY WALLET.

57:54.345 --> 57:57.056
I COULD READ YOU
WHAT MY RIGHTS ARE.

57:57.056 --> 57:59.100
YOU'LL BE READING IT FROM
THAT CAGE.

57:59.100 --> 58:02.187
WE'LL COME BACK IN THREE HOURS
AND ASK YOU THE SAME QUESTIONS.

58:02.187 --> 58:04.731
I WAS OUT...

58:04.731 --> 58:08.276
WANDERING AROUND,
NOTHING MUCH -- NO BIG DEAL.

58:08.276 --> 58:09.611
STOP BY YOUR GRANDMA'S?

58:09.611 --> 58:10.778
NO.

58:10.778 --> 58:12.489
WE FOUND HER, JERRY.

58:12.489 --> 58:13.865
YEAH, WHERE?

58:13.865 --> 58:15.867
IN HER APARTMENT, MURDERED.

58:15.867 --> 58:19.496
[ SCOFFS ] YEAH, NO WAY.

58:19.496 --> 58:20.538
YEAH.

58:22.790 --> 58:24.167
ARE YOU GUYS SERIOUS?

58:24.167 --> 58:29.130
JERRY...DO YOU KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THIS?

58:29.130 --> 58:30.924
SHE'S REALLY DEAD?

58:30.924 --> 58:32.550
YES, SHE'S DEAD.

58:32.550 --> 58:35.553
SHE'S NOT -- SHE CAN'T --
SHE'S NOT DEAD.

58:35.553 --> 58:36.930
SHE CAN'T BE DEAD.

58:36.930 --> 58:39.265
DID YOU GO BY YOUR GRANDMA'S
TO GET SOME MONEY

58:39.265 --> 58:40.517
AND SHE TURNED YOU DOWN?

58:40.517 --> 58:43.686
LARRY SOMEBODY -- THIS GUY
WHO LIVED ON HER FLOOR.

58:43.686 --> 58:45.563
HE'S AN EX-CON.

58:45.563 --> 58:47.315
I TOLD HER
NOT TO HANG AROUND WITH HIM,

58:47.315 --> 58:49.192
BUT SHE SAID
THAT HE CHANGED.

58:49.192 --> 58:51.653
SHE'S A CHRISTIAN.
SHE'S INTO FORGIVENESS.

58:51.653 --> 58:53.780
BUT I TOLD HER. I TOLD
HER!

58:53.780 --> 58:56.699
I CAN'T BELIEVE SHE'S DEAD.

58:56.699 --> 58:58.868
DID YOU HURT YOUR GRANDMOTHER
THIS MORNING?!

58:58.868 --> 59:00.036
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

59:00.036 --> 59:01.871
ANSWER THE QUESTION, JERRY!

59:01.871 --> 59:03.373
NO, I DIDN'T HURT HER!

59:03.373 --> 59:06.042
SHE WAS MY ANGEL.
SHE WAS MY BEST FRIEND.

59:12.799 --> 59:14.634
ANYTHING FROM THE BAR?

59:14.634 --> 59:16.803
YEAH, A FRIEND OF CATHERINE'S.

59:16.803 --> 59:18.846
SHE WAS THERE WEDNESDAY NIGHT AT
O'DELL'S

59:18.846 --> 59:20.640
AND SAID THAT CATHERINE
WAS UPSET

59:20.640 --> 59:22.892
OVER THE BREAKUP
WITH HER BOYFRIEND, STEVE.

59:22.892 --> 59:24.143
REASON THEY BROKE UP IS

59:24.143 --> 59:26.896
THAT STEVE SMACKED HER SON,
SCOTT, DURING AN ARGUMENT.

59:29.148 --> 59:30.942
WE'RE GRABBING HIM UP.

59:30.942 --> 59:34.362
YEAH.

59:34.362 --> 59:36.030
WHAT'S UP WITH THE GRANDSON?

59:36.030 --> 59:38.199
HE TOOK THE NEWS OF HER DEATH
PRETTY HARD.

59:38.199 --> 59:40.368
RITA'S GETTING WHERE HE WAS
TODAY.

59:40.368 --> 59:41.703
THEN, WE'LL VERIFY IT.

59:41.703 --> 59:43.204
CAN YOU HOLD HIM?

59:43.204 --> 59:45.748
WE DON'T HAVE ENOUGH.
PLUS, HE'S DEMANDING TO LEAVE.

59:45.748 --> 59:48.626
GOT AN ACLU RIGHTS CARD,
WHICH HE'S QUOTING FROM.

59:48.626 --> 59:51.629
CAN YOU GET YOUR HANDS ON HIM
IF YOU NEED TO AGAIN?

59:51.629 --> 59:53.965
YEAH.

59:53.965 --> 59:56.384
HI, I'M OFFICER ANDERSON
FROM THE BOROUGH

59:56.384 --> 59:57.844
TO AUDIT THE TIME RECORDS.

59:57.844 --> 59:59.762
SURE, LET ME GET THEM
FOR YOU.

59:59.762 --> 1:00:00.888
HI.

1:00:00.888 --> 1:00:03.266
HEY, HOW'S IT GOING? NEED SOME
HELP?

1:00:03.266 --> 1:00:05.435
OH, NO, I'VE BEEN HELPED.
THANKS.

1:00:05.435 --> 1:00:07.895
I'M MAYA ANDERSON. I WORK
IN THE 2-5.

1:00:07.895 --> 1:00:10.982
BUT I'M ON RESTRICTED DUTY,
AUDITING TIME RECORDS.

1:00:10.982 --> 1:00:13.234
BALDWIN JONES.
LINE-OF-DUTY INJURY?

1:00:13.234 --> 1:00:16.112
I WAS RUNNING SOME TRAILS
AND LANDED ON A TREE ROOT.

1:00:16.112 --> 1:00:17.822
I TORE MY KNEE UP.

1:00:17.822 --> 1:00:20.700
I SHOULD BE BACK TO FULL DUTY
IN THE NEXT COUPLE OF WEEKS.

1:00:20.700 --> 1:00:22.285
HERE'S OUR TIME RECORDS.

1:00:22.285 --> 1:00:24.412
ANYTHING ELSE?

1:00:24.412 --> 1:00:26.497
UH, NO, I GUESS NOT.

1:00:26.497 --> 1:00:29.042
WELL, NICE TO MEET YOU.
FEEL BETTER.

1:00:29.042 --> 1:00:32.503
YOU TOO.
UM, I MEAN, THANKS.

1:00:39.052 --> 1:00:40.928
I AIN'T A YO-YO, GUYS.

1:00:40.928 --> 1:00:42.680
THIS IS STARTING TO GET OLD.

1:00:42.680 --> 1:00:45.600
STEVE, DID YOU HAVE A PROBLEM
WITH SCOTT LOWE?

1:00:45.600 --> 1:00:46.601
NO.

1:00:46.601 --> 1:00:47.894
YOU PUT YOUR HANDS ON HIM?

1:00:47.894 --> 1:00:49.437
NO!

1:00:49.437 --> 1:00:51.397
THAT FIGHT
YOU BROKE UP OVER

1:00:51.397 --> 1:00:53.691
WASN'T ABOUT YOU
SMACKING SCOTT?!

1:00:53.691 --> 1:00:54.942
DON'T LIE TO US!

1:00:54.942 --> 1:00:56.444
ME AND CATH GOT
IN AN ARGUMENT.

1:00:56.444 --> 1:00:59.030
SCOTT STARTED SCREAMING AT ME
AND SLAPPING AT ME.

1:00:59.030 --> 1:01:00.657
DID YOU PUT YOUR HANDS
ON HIM?!

1:01:00.657 --> 1:01:02.825
A LITTLE BACKHAND --
A LITTLE SLAP, ONCE.

1:01:02.825 --> 1:01:03.951
GET ON YOUR FEET!

1:01:03.951 --> 1:01:04.952
THAT'S ALL!

1:01:04.952 --> 1:01:06.162
GET ON YOUR FEET!

1:01:06.162 --> 1:01:07.830
GET YOUR HANDS OFF OF ME!

1:01:07.830 --> 1:01:09.165
I'VE HAD IT WITH YOU!

1:01:09.165 --> 1:01:10.541
I'VE HAD IT WITH YOU, TOO!

1:01:10.541 --> 1:01:12.669
TELL US WHAT HAPPENED
TWO NIGHTS AGO!

1:01:12.669 --> 1:01:14.170
YOU GET YOUR HANDS OFF OF
ME!

1:01:14.170 --> 1:01:16.005
YOU'RE NOT LEAVING
UNTIL YOU TELL US!

1:01:16.005 --> 1:01:17.131
I'M WARNING YOU.

1:01:17.131 --> 1:01:18.466
ABOUT WHAT?!

1:01:18.466 --> 1:01:20.635
GET OFF OF ME!

1:01:22.804 --> 1:01:24.472
ANDY, ANDY!

1:01:24.472 --> 1:01:25.973
GET OFF OF ME!

1:01:28.810 --> 1:01:32.897
I DIDN'T DO IT!

1:01:32.897 --> 1:01:34.440
I DIDN'T DO IT!!

1:01:34.440 --> 1:01:36.359
GET UP.

1:01:36.359 --> 1:01:38.277
GET HIM IN A CHAIR.

1:01:38.277 --> 1:01:39.487
I DIDN'T DO IT!

1:01:39.487 --> 1:01:41.989
TELL US! I'LL KEEP HIM AWAY
FROM YOU.

1:01:41.989 --> 1:01:43.032
I DIDN'T KILL SCOTT!

1:01:43.032 --> 1:01:44.701
WE'RE HOLDING YOU
FOR ASSAULT!

1:01:44.701 --> 1:01:46.953
WE'RE GONNA KEEP ON GOING
TILL YOU TELL US!

1:01:46.953 --> 1:01:48.538
I DIDN'T DO NOTHING
TO THAT KID!

1:01:48.538 --> 1:01:50.289
YOU UNDERSTAND ME?!
I DIDN'T DO IT!

1:01:50.289 --> 1:01:51.499
ENOUGH!

1:01:51.499 --> 1:01:52.875
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

1:02:05.304 --> 1:02:06.597
BOYFRIEND'S DUG IN.

1:02:06.597 --> 1:02:09.642
WE'RE GONNA GIVE HIM
A LITTLE TIME TO COOL OFF.

1:02:09.642 --> 1:02:11.018
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

1:02:11.018 --> 1:02:12.520
HE RESISTED.

1:02:12.520 --> 1:02:14.313
DON'T TELL ME YOU TUNED
THIS GUY UP.

1:02:14.313 --> 1:02:15.773
HE RESISTED.
HE CAME AT ME.

1:02:15.773 --> 1:02:16.983
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

1:02:16.983 --> 1:02:17.984
YEAH.

1:02:17.984 --> 1:02:19.652
DANZIG --
IS HE BANGED UP BAD?

1:02:19.652 --> 1:02:22.029
NO. I GOT IN ONE OR TWO.
THEN JUNIOR JUMPED IN.

1:02:22.029 --> 1:02:24.699
PHONE DUMP CAME BACK
FROM CATHERINE LOWE'S APARTMENT.

1:02:24.699 --> 1:02:26.325
THE NIGHT
HER SON WENT MISSING,

1:02:26.325 --> 1:02:28.703
THERE WERE TWO CALLS IN FROM
THE DWYER HOUSE --

1:02:28.703 --> 1:02:30.663
ONE AT 8:15 AND 8:30 P.M.

1:02:30.663 --> 1:02:32.540
TOMMY DWYER'S THE EX-COP

1:02:32.540 --> 1:02:35.293
WHOSE SON WAS
THE D.O.A.'s FRIEND.

1:02:35.293 --> 1:02:36.294
YEP.

1:02:36.294 --> 1:02:37.670
DID WE TALK TO THE SON?

1:02:37.670 --> 1:02:39.964
TOMMY SAID HIS KID
DIDN'T KNOW NOTHING.

1:02:39.964 --> 1:02:41.215
Tony: GET OVER THERE.

1:02:41.215 --> 1:02:43.176
CAN YOU GET DANZIG
TO A CELL DOWNSTAIRS?

1:02:43.176 --> 1:02:44.218
YEAH, SURE.

1:02:44.218 --> 1:02:45.845
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

1:02:45.845 --> 1:02:47.263
YEAH, I'M FINE.

1:02:47.263 --> 1:02:49.682
LATENT PRINT GOT A HIT
OFF A FOOTBALL HELMET

1:02:49.682 --> 1:02:51.559
ON SCOTT LOWE'S
BEDROOM DRESSER.

1:02:51.559 --> 1:02:53.060
COMES BACK TO A RICK SAVRAN.

1:02:53.060 --> 1:02:55.772
HE COMES BACK WITH A COUPLE
OF PRIORS FOR BURGLARY.

1:02:55.772 --> 1:02:58.316
HIS NAME COME UP IN THE
INTERVIEWS WITH THE MOTHER?

1:02:58.316 --> 1:02:59.567
NO.

1:02:59.567 --> 1:03:01.903
WHAT'S IT GONNA TAKE
TO GET THESE PEOPLE

1:03:01.903 --> 1:03:03.488
TO START TELLING THE TRUTH?

1:03:03.488 --> 1:03:06.032
[ SIGHS ]

1:03:12.955 --> 1:03:14.123
HEY.

1:03:14.123 --> 1:03:15.333
HOW'S IT GOING, TOMMY?

1:03:15.333 --> 1:03:16.626
OKAY. WHAT'S UP?

1:03:16.626 --> 1:03:18.669
WE NEED TO TALK TO JAKE.

1:03:18.669 --> 1:03:19.670
ABOUT SCOTT?

1:03:19.670 --> 1:03:21.130
YEAH.

1:03:21.130 --> 1:03:23.424
HE DON'T KNOW ANYTHING.
I'VE ASKED HIM 10 TIMES.

1:03:23.424 --> 1:03:25.301
TOMMY, JAKE WAS
HIS BEST FRIEND.

1:03:25.301 --> 1:03:26.427
WE GOTTA ASK.

1:03:26.427 --> 1:03:28.429
OH, YEAH, SURE, I
UNDERSTAND.

1:03:28.429 --> 1:03:29.972
I'M IN THE ROOM, THOUGH.

1:03:29.972 --> 1:03:31.098
OKAY.

1:03:34.185 --> 1:03:37.772
JAKE, COME HERE, PAL.

1:03:40.233 --> 1:03:41.609
THESE ARE DETECTIVES.

1:03:41.609 --> 1:03:43.694
THEY'RE GONNA ASK YOU
SOME QUESTIONS.

1:03:43.694 --> 1:03:45.696
HI, JAKE. DETECTIVE
CLARK, SIPOWICZ.

1:03:45.696 --> 1:03:48.282
DID SCOTT MENTION ANYBODY
HE WAS AFRAID OF --

1:03:48.282 --> 1:03:50.201
ANYBODY WHO WANTED
TO HURT HIM?

1:03:50.201 --> 1:03:52.161
HIS MOM'S BOYFRIEND, STEVE.

1:03:52.161 --> 1:03:54.413
DID SCOTT<i> SAY</i>
STEVE WANTED TO HURT HIM?

1:03:54.413 --> 1:03:55.998
I DON'T KNOW. I GUESS.

1:03:55.998 --> 1:03:57.834
IT'S IMPORTANT
YOU TRY AND REMEMBER.

1:03:57.834 --> 1:04:00.419
HE DIDN'T LIKE STEVE.
THAT'S BASICALLY WHAT HE SAID.

1:04:00.419 --> 1:04:03.422
DID YOU TRY CALLING SCOTT AT
HIS APARTMENT WEDNESDAY NIGHT?

1:04:03.422 --> 1:04:04.966
NO.
YOU SURE?

1:04:04.966 --> 1:04:06.843
HE'S SURE.
HE JUST TOLD YOU.

1:04:06.843 --> 1:04:08.636
TOMMY, DID YOU CALL
THEIR APARTMENT?

1:04:08.636 --> 1:04:09.679
NO.

1:04:09.679 --> 1:04:11.430
Andy: JAKE,
DO YOU KNOW ANYTHING

1:04:11.430 --> 1:04:12.849
ABOUT HOW SCOTT GOT KILLED?

1:04:12.849 --> 1:04:14.058
NO.

1:04:14.058 --> 1:04:15.601
THIS WAS YOUR BEST FRIEND,
JAKE.

1:04:15.601 --> 1:04:16.853
OKAY, THAT'S IT.

1:04:16.853 --> 1:04:19.272
GO PLAY AT EDDIE'S. WAIT TO
HEAR FROM ME.

1:04:19.272 --> 1:04:20.356
OKAY.

1:04:20.356 --> 1:04:23.401
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

1:04:23.401 --> 1:04:25.653
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS,
BADGERING MY KID?

1:04:25.653 --> 1:04:27.029
THERE WERE TWO PHONE CALLS

1:04:27.029 --> 1:04:29.156
FROM THIS APARTMENT TO THE
LOWES' WEDNESDAY NIGHT.

1:04:29.156 --> 1:04:30.408
SO?

1:04:30.408 --> 1:04:31.868
WHO MADE THEM?

1:04:31.868 --> 1:04:34.996
I TRY TO DO THE RIGHT THING AND
HELP YOU GUYS OUT,

1:04:34.996 --> 1:04:36.998
AND YOU AMBUSH ME
AND MY KID?

1:04:36.998 --> 1:04:38.541
WHO MADE THE PHONE CALLS,
TOMMY?

1:04:38.541 --> 1:04:39.917
I DON'T KNOW!

1:04:39.917 --> 1:04:41.836
MAYBE JAKE MADE THEM BUT HE
FORGOT!

1:04:41.836 --> 1:04:44.255
IT'S NOT LIKE HE'S NOT
BORDERLINE TRAUMATIZED

1:04:44.255 --> 1:04:46.132
WITH HIS FRIEND
GETTING MURDERED!

1:04:47.675 --> 1:04:49.886
OH, WHAT,<i> I'M </i>GETTING
EYEBALLED NOW?!

1:04:49.886 --> 1:04:53.014
LISTEN TO ME -- MY SON
DOESN'T KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT IT.

1:04:53.014 --> 1:04:55.975
AND THAT'S FROM A GUY
WHO DID 20 YEARS ON YOUR JOB.

1:04:55.975 --> 1:04:58.436
I TOLD JAKE TO KEEP HIS EARS
OPEN IN SCHOOL.

1:04:58.436 --> 1:05:01.022
IF HE HEARS ANYTHING, I'LL
PASS IT ALONG.

1:05:01.022 --> 1:05:02.189
NOW WE'RE DONE.

1:05:12.575 --> 1:05:15.453
HAVE YOU HAD
ANY PROGRESS?

1:05:15.453 --> 1:05:16.537
A LITTLE.

1:05:18.748 --> 1:05:20.082
PLEASE JUST TELL ME

1:05:20.082 --> 1:05:22.668
THAT HE WASN'T MOLESTED
BEFORE HE WAS KILLED.

1:05:22.668 --> 1:05:25.046
JUST TELL ME
THAT SCOTT DIDN'T SUFFER.

1:05:25.046 --> 1:05:26.881
THERE'S NOTHING
TO INDICATE THAT.

1:05:26.881 --> 1:05:28.049
THANK GOD.

1:05:28.049 --> 1:05:29.800
MS. LOWE, WE GOT
A FINGERPRINT HIT

1:05:29.800 --> 1:05:31.802
OFF A FOOTBALL HELMET IN YOUR
SON'S ROOM.

1:05:31.802 --> 1:05:32.970
FROM WHO?

1:05:32.970 --> 1:05:34.597
A RICK SAVRAN.

1:05:34.597 --> 1:05:36.223
DO YOU KNOW HIM?

1:05:36.223 --> 1:05:38.351
DO YOU KNOW HIM,
MS. LOWE?

1:05:38.351 --> 1:05:40.227
YEAH, I KNOW RICK.

1:05:40.227 --> 1:05:41.520
HOW?

1:05:41.520 --> 1:05:44.231
UM, HE'S A FRIEND
OF MY BOYFRIEND STEVE'S.

1:05:44.231 --> 1:05:45.524
WHEN WAS HE OVER HERE?

1:05:45.524 --> 1:05:46.734
ABOUT A WEEK AGO.

1:05:46.734 --> 1:05:48.903
DON'T TELL STEVE
THAT RICK WAS OVER HERE.

1:05:48.903 --> 1:05:50.029
IT WOULD LOOK WRONG.

1:05:50.029 --> 1:05:51.739
'CAUSE RICK SAVRAN
SPENT THE NIGHT?

1:05:51.739 --> 1:05:53.157
THAT'S NONE
OF YOUR BUSINESS.

1:05:53.157 --> 1:05:56.410
MS. LOWE, YOU NEED TO TELL US
WHO'S BEEN IN THIS APARTMENT!

1:05:56.410 --> 1:05:57.870
RICK SPENT THE NIGHT<i> ONCE.</i>

1:05:57.870 --> 1:05:59.997
SCOTT WAS SLEEPING
AT A FRIEND'S HOUSE.

1:05:59.997 --> 1:06:01.499
RICK WOULD NOT KILL SCOTT!

1:06:01.499 --> 1:06:04.210
I DON'T UNDERSTAND WHY
WE GOTTA BRING HIM INTO THIS!

1:06:04.210 --> 1:06:06.045
HAVE ANY OTHER MEN
SPENT THE NIGHT

1:06:06.045 --> 1:06:08.172
OR BEEN OVER HERE
IN THE LAST FEW MONTHS?

1:06:08.172 --> 1:06:10.800
PHIL WESTON.
I WORK WITH HIM.

1:06:10.800 --> 1:06:12.677
WE'LL NEED TO SPEAK WITH BOTH
OF THEM.

1:06:12.677 --> 1:06:14.470
YOU WANNA HEAR
THE DIRTY DETAILS?!

1:06:14.470 --> 1:06:16.764
WE'RE NOT TRYING
TO CAUSE YOU EMBARRASSMENT,

1:06:16.764 --> 1:06:18.766
BUT WE NEED TO KNOW WHAT MEN
HAVE BEEN

1:06:18.766 --> 1:06:21.227
IN THIS APARTMENT, 'CAUSE
WHEN KIDS GET MURDERED,

1:06:21.227 --> 1:06:23.270
IT'S USUALLY BY MEN
WHO KNEW THE VICTIM!

1:06:23.270 --> 1:06:25.189
PHIL AND RICK --
THAT'S IT!

1:06:25.189 --> 1:06:26.565
THAT'S ALL THERE WAS!

1:06:26.565 --> 1:06:28.734
ARE YOU PROTECTING ANYONE,
MS. LOWE?

1:06:28.734 --> 1:06:31.028
GET OUT OF MY APARTMENT!
NOW! GET OUT!

1:06:40.037 --> 1:06:41.288
DETECTIVE ORTIZ.

1:06:43.499 --> 1:06:45.710
WE NEED A SEARCH WARRANT
ON DWYER'S APARTMENT.

1:06:45.710 --> 1:06:47.503
BASED ON WHAT?

1:06:47.503 --> 1:06:50.297
TWO PHONE CALLS TO THE D.O.A.'s
THE NIGHT HE WENT MISSING.

1:06:50.297 --> 1:06:53.467
BOTH THE DAD AND SON SAID
THEY DIDN'T MAKE ANY CALLS.

1:06:53.467 --> 1:06:54.719
WERE THERE MESSAGES?

1:06:54.719 --> 1:06:55.886
NO.

1:06:55.886 --> 1:06:57.722
WHAT WAS THE DAD
AND SON'S EXCUSE?

1:06:57.722 --> 1:07:00.474
THE DAD GOT BELLIGERENT,
SAID HIS SON MIGHT HAVE FORGOT.

1:07:00.474 --> 1:07:02.810
THERE'S NO WAY YOU FORGET
ABOUT TWO CALLS.

1:07:02.810 --> 1:07:04.395
WE NEED A SEARCH WARRANT

1:07:04.395 --> 1:07:07.523
SO WE CAN HAVE CRIME SCENE
PROCESS THE APARTMENT.

1:07:07.523 --> 1:07:09.900
CAN YOU CALL COURT
AND EXPEDITE IT?

1:07:09.900 --> 1:07:12.945
YEAH. SWING BY THERE
AND SWEAR TO THE AFFIDAVIT.

1:07:12.945 --> 1:07:14.071
THANKS.

1:07:18.325 --> 1:07:21.495
THAT WAS THE SUPER AT
THE ELDERLY D.O.A.'s BUILDING.

1:07:21.495 --> 1:07:23.372
HE SAID THE GRANDSON, JERRY
GAVIOLA,

1:07:23.372 --> 1:07:24.582
SHOWED UP 10 MINUTES AGO

1:07:24.582 --> 1:07:26.709
AND WENT INTO
HIS GRANDMOTHER'S APARTMENT.

1:07:26.709 --> 1:07:28.294
ISN'T THE APARTMENT SEALED?

1:07:28.294 --> 1:07:30.421
HE RIPPED
THE CRIME-SCENE TAPE OFF.

1:07:30.421 --> 1:07:33.049
WE BETTER HEAD OVER THERE
AND SEE WHAT'S GOING ON.

1:07:33.049 --> 1:07:34.133
YEAH.

1:07:36.469 --> 1:07:38.304
DID THE MOM KNOW
RICK SAVRAN?

1:07:38.304 --> 1:07:40.097
YEAH, BANGED HIM A WEEK
AGO.

1:07:40.097 --> 1:07:42.308
SHE BANGING ANYBODY ELSE?

1:07:42.308 --> 1:07:44.602
CO-WORKER.
WE'RE ON IT.

1:07:44.602 --> 1:07:47.730
HEY.
HEY.

1:07:47.730 --> 1:07:51.275
HI. I NEED A MINUTE
WITH DETECTIVE JONES.

1:07:51.275 --> 1:07:53.277
OKAY.

1:07:57.865 --> 1:07:59.492
UH, DETECTIVE JONES?

1:07:59.492 --> 1:08:02.536
YEAH? MAYA.

1:08:02.536 --> 1:08:04.330
VERY GOOD. YOU REMEMBERED.

1:08:04.330 --> 1:08:05.831
UH, REAL QUICK.

1:08:05.831 --> 1:08:07.458
THREE WEEKS AGO,

1:08:07.458 --> 1:08:11.212
YOUR TIMECARD SAYS
YOU WORKED UNTIL 1815.

1:08:11.212 --> 1:08:14.507
OUR RECORDS AT THE BOROUGH
HAVE YOUR TOUR ENDING AT 1800.

1:08:14.507 --> 1:08:17.259
THAT'S 15 MINUTES
UNACCOUNTED FOR.

1:08:17.259 --> 1:08:20.179
NOW, WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO
ABOUT THIS?

1:08:20.179 --> 1:08:22.681
[ CHUCKLES ]
UH, MAYA...

1:08:22.681 --> 1:08:23.974
YES, DETECTIVE?

1:08:23.974 --> 1:08:27.269
I'M IN THE MIDDLE OF A
REALLY IMPORTANT CASE.

1:08:27.269 --> 1:08:29.980
OH. OKAY.

1:08:29.980 --> 1:08:32.358
I'M SORRY.

1:08:32.358 --> 1:08:35.069
MAYBE SOME OTHER TIME.

1:08:35.069 --> 1:08:39.031
YEAH, I'D, UM,
I'D LET THIS SLIDE IF I COULD,

1:08:39.031 --> 1:08:40.241
BUT I CAN'T.

1:08:40.241 --> 1:08:42.660
SEE, THAT'S 15 MINUTES
OF TAXPAYER MONEY

1:08:42.660 --> 1:08:43.869
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT.

1:08:43.869 --> 1:08:45.287
[ CHUCKLES ]

1:08:45.287 --> 1:08:47.331
THEY'RE ON THEIR WAY OVER TO
PICK IT UP.

1:08:47.331 --> 1:08:49.333
I'LL HOLD.

1:08:49.333 --> 1:08:50.626
Whew!

1:08:50.626 --> 1:08:51.669
WHAT?

1:08:51.669 --> 1:08:53.504
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THAT WAS ABOUT.

1:08:53.504 --> 1:08:55.089
I THINK YOU GOT
A GOOD IDEA.

1:08:55.089 --> 1:08:56.298
I'M SERIOUS.

1:08:56.298 --> 1:08:58.843
NOT AROUND ME, BALDWIN.
I'M NOT READY FOR THAT.

1:08:58.843 --> 1:08:59.969
VALERIE...

1:08:59.969 --> 1:09:03.097
YEAH, I'M RIGHT HERE.
UH-HUH.

1:09:13.899 --> 1:09:15.234
WHAT?

1:09:15.234 --> 1:09:17.903
WE GOT A SEARCH WARRANT, TOMMY.
WE NEED TO COME INSIDE.

1:09:17.903 --> 1:09:19.071
FOR WHAT?

1:09:19.071 --> 1:09:20.823
WE'RE GONNA PROCESS
THE APARTMENT.

1:09:20.823 --> 1:09:22.575
WE'RE SUSPECTS?

1:09:22.575 --> 1:09:24.785
WE'RE GONNA PROCESS
EVERY PLACE SCOTT'S BEEN.

1:09:24.785 --> 1:09:26.662
OH, YOU GUYS ARE...

1:09:26.662 --> 1:09:29.498
[ SIGHS ] LET ME SEE IT.

1:09:31.542 --> 1:09:33.294
IT'S ALL THERE.

1:09:33.294 --> 1:09:35.796
TOMMY, DON'T TURN THIS
INTO SOMETHING.

1:09:35.796 --> 1:09:38.132
YOU'RE THE ONES
TURNING THIS INTO SOMETHING.

1:09:38.132 --> 1:09:40.217
LET'S GO, GUYS.

1:09:45.598 --> 1:09:48.601
HE STILL WON'T OPEN
THE DOOR.

1:09:48.601 --> 1:09:51.270
JERRY?

1:09:51.270 --> 1:09:53.272
OPEN THE DOOR.

1:09:53.272 --> 1:09:55.733
DETECTIVES McDOWELL
AND ORTIZ.

1:09:55.733 --> 1:09:57.359
OPEN THE DOOR, JERRY.

1:10:00.154 --> 1:10:02.031
YOU GOT A KEY?

1:10:02.031 --> 1:10:03.032
YEAH.

1:10:03.032 --> 1:10:04.575
OPEN IT.

1:10:15.336 --> 1:10:17.546
[ GASPS ] OH, GOD.

1:10:17.546 --> 1:10:20.591
HELP ME OUT.

1:10:20.591 --> 1:10:22.259
UGH.

1:10:26.263 --> 1:10:27.431
HE'S COLD.

1:10:27.431 --> 1:10:29.934
LET ME PUT A RUSH
ON A BUS ANYWAY.

1:10:29.934 --> 1:10:32.937
50 SQUAD TO CENTRAL "K."

1:10:32.937 --> 1:10:36.899
PUT A RUSH ON A BUS --
2403 AVENUE "D."

1:10:39.568 --> 1:10:41.737
"I DIDN'T KILL MY GRANDMA."

1:10:44.031 --> 1:10:45.658
[ SIGHS ]

1:10:45.658 --> 1:10:46.700
ORTIZ.

1:10:46.700 --> 1:10:47.868
BACK UP, OKAY?

1:10:47.868 --> 1:10:49.620
I WOULD HAVE OPENED
THE DOOR SOONER

1:10:49.620 --> 1:10:51.121
IF I'D HAVE KNOWN
HE WAS GONNA DO THIS.

1:10:51.121 --> 1:10:52.915
IT'S OKAY.

1:10:52.915 --> 1:10:55.751
COME ON, COME ON. IT'S ALL
RIGHT.

1:10:55.751 --> 1:10:58.671
M.E. SAID SHE WAS RAPED, THEN
STRANGLED.

1:10:58.671 --> 1:11:01.006
WE GOTTA BRING IN THIS LARRY
REAL EASY.

1:11:01.006 --> 1:11:02.633
JUST WAIT THERE, OKAY,
GUYS?

1:11:02.633 --> 1:11:04.468
OKAY.

1:11:12.268 --> 1:11:14.311
HOW MUCH LONGER
IS THIS GONNA BE?

1:11:14.311 --> 1:11:15.854
A LITTLE WHILE LONGER.

1:11:15.854 --> 1:11:17.064
IT'S EMBARRASSING!

1:11:17.064 --> 1:11:18.274
YOU GUYS' CARS ARE

1:11:18.274 --> 1:11:20.276
OUT IN FRONT
OF THE BUILDING!

1:11:20.276 --> 1:11:23.654
WE JUST WANT TO DO IT RIGHT
SO WE DON'T HAVE TO COME BACK.

1:11:23.654 --> 1:11:25.406
HEY, ANDY, THEY'RE READY.

1:11:25.406 --> 1:11:27.032
NO, YOU WAIT HERE.

1:11:32.913 --> 1:11:34.039
Junior: THE LIGHT.

1:11:36.458 --> 1:11:39.461
WELL, THIS IS
OUR CRIME SCENE.

1:11:54.101 --> 1:11:56.103
JUST TELL US
WHAT HAPPENED, TOMMY.

1:11:56.103 --> 1:11:59.773
I WILL, BUT YOU GOTTA PROMISE
THAT THIS WILL LAND ON<i> ME.</i>

1:11:59.773 --> 1:12:01.442
LEAVE MY SON OUT OF IT.

1:12:01.442 --> 1:12:04.069
WE CAN'T DO ANYTHING
TILL WE KNOW WHAT HAPPENED.

1:12:04.069 --> 1:12:06.238
SCOTT WAS OVER.

1:12:06.238 --> 1:12:09.533
I WENT OUT TO GET SOME PIZZAS,
RENT SOME VIDEO GAMES.

1:12:09.533 --> 1:12:12.036
I WAS GONE A HALF-HOUR, AT
THE MOST.

1:12:12.036 --> 1:12:14.872
I NEVER HID MY GUNS
FROM JAKE.

1:12:14.872 --> 1:12:16.790
LIKE THEY TELL YOU IN THE
ACADEMY,

1:12:16.790 --> 1:12:19.209
"DON'T MAKE YOUR GUNS
A MYSTERY TO YOUR KIDS."

1:12:19.209 --> 1:12:22.129
IF HE WANTED, I'D UNLOAD IT
AND LET HIM HOLD IT.

1:12:28.218 --> 1:12:31.430
JAKE SAID THAT SCOTT HAD BEEN
AFTER HIM TO SEE THE GUN.

1:12:31.430 --> 1:12:33.349
SO JAKE WENT IN THE CLOSET
AND GOT IT.

1:12:33.349 --> 1:12:35.851
AND SCOTT WANTED
TO PUT THE CLIP IN,

1:12:35.851 --> 1:12:37.102
SO JAKE DID.

1:12:37.102 --> 1:12:39.355
AND THEY TOOK TURNS
SNAPPING THE CLIP IN

1:12:39.355 --> 1:12:40.439
AND HEAR THE CLICK.

1:12:40.439 --> 1:12:41.899
BUT JAKE TOOK THE CLIP OUT.

1:12:41.899 --> 1:12:44.276
AND THEN THEY STARTED
PLAYING WITH IT AGAIN.

1:12:47.196 --> 1:12:49.865
[ Crying] HE DIDN'T KNOW...

1:12:49.865 --> 1:12:55.454
I KEEP ONE IN THE CHAMBER.

1:12:55.454 --> 1:12:57.831
I GOT THERE
10 MINUTES AFTER IT HAPPENED,

1:12:57.831 --> 1:12:58.999
AND SCOTT WAS DEAD.

1:12:58.999 --> 1:13:01.835
WHEN DID YOU BURY SCOTT?

1:13:01.835 --> 1:13:02.836
THAT NIGHT.

1:13:02.836 --> 1:13:05.297
THERE WAS NOTHING
WE COULD DO.

1:13:05.297 --> 1:13:07.716
AND THERE WAS NO WAY
I WAS TAKING A CHANCE

1:13:07.716 --> 1:13:10.052
AT MY SON DOING TIME
IN A YOUTH FACILITY.

1:13:10.052 --> 1:13:11.220
HE WOULDN'T MAKE IT.

1:13:11.220 --> 1:13:13.764
DID YOU GIVE HALF A THOUGHT
TO THE INVESTIGATION?

1:13:13.764 --> 1:13:15.849
OF COURSE I DID, AND I
WANT IT KNOWN

1:13:15.849 --> 1:13:18.143
I PUT SCOTT IN A PLACE
WHERE HE'D BE FOUND

1:13:18.143 --> 1:13:20.104
SO HE COULD HAVE
A PROPER FUNERAL.

1:13:20.104 --> 1:13:21.522
I COULD HAVE MADE IT

1:13:21.522 --> 1:13:23.899
SO THAT HIS BODY NEVER
WOULD HAVE BEEN RECOVERED.

1:13:23.899 --> 1:13:26.568
MEANWHILE, WE'RE RIPPING
HIS FAMILY'S GUTS OUT,

1:13:26.568 --> 1:13:28.862
FIGURING ONE OF THEM
TO BE THE KILLER!

1:13:28.862 --> 1:13:30.364
I'M LOOKING OUT
FOR MY SON!

1:13:30.364 --> 1:13:32.366
BY TEACHING HIM
HOW TO COVER THINGS UP?

1:13:32.366 --> 1:13:35.202
TURNING HIM INTO
A CO-CONSPIRATOR
IN A CRIMINAL ACT?

1:13:38.330 --> 1:13:40.374
WE'RE GONNA NEED
TO TALK TO JAKE NOW.

1:13:40.374 --> 1:13:43.669
PUT THIS ON ME --
FAILURE TO SAFEGUARD A GUN,

1:13:43.669 --> 1:13:46.630
TAMPERING WITH EVIDENCE,
DISPOSAL OF A BODY.

1:13:46.630 --> 1:13:49.425
PUT IT ALL ON ME,
BUT DON'T CHARGE MY SON.

1:13:49.425 --> 1:13:52.469
UNFORTUNATELY, THAT'S NOT GONNA
HAPPEN, MR. DWYER.

1:13:52.469 --> 1:13:53.971
IF YOUR ACCOUNT IS TRUE,

1:13:53.971 --> 1:13:56.682
JAKE WILL BE ARRESTED
FOR SECOND-DEGREE MANSLAUGHTER,

1:13:56.682 --> 1:13:58.767
AND IT'LL BE HANDLED
IN FAMILY COURT.

1:13:58.767 --> 1:14:01.103
I CAN'T GET ANY
CONSIDERATION?

1:14:01.103 --> 1:14:03.063
20 YEARS I PUT ON THIS JOB!

1:14:03.063 --> 1:14:05.441
IF THE FACTS YOU RELAYED HOLD
TRUE,

1:14:05.441 --> 1:14:08.694
MY OFFICE WILL RECOMMEND
TO THE CORPORATION COUNSEL

1:14:08.694 --> 1:14:12.197
THAT NO PERIOD OF INCARCERATION
WILL BE IMPOSED ON JAKE.

1:14:12.197 --> 1:14:14.575
BUT HE WILL BE ARRESTED
AND CHARGED.

1:14:20.456 --> 1:14:22.124
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

1:14:24.835 --> 1:14:26.378
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

1:14:26.378 --> 1:14:28.797
WELL, YOU SHOULD HAVE
LEFT IT AT THAT.

1:14:38.307 --> 1:14:41.018
THE MEDICAL-EXAMINER REPORT
CAME BACK, LARRY.

1:14:41.018 --> 1:14:43.395
MRS. GAVIOLA WAS RAPED.

1:14:43.395 --> 1:14:45.189
BY HER GRANDSON?

1:14:45.189 --> 1:14:47.399
WE HIGHLY DOUBT THAT.

1:14:47.399 --> 1:14:50.152
WELL, YOU NEVER KNOW
WHAT SOME PEOPLE ARE CAPABLE OF.

1:14:50.152 --> 1:14:52.237
WE'RE GONNA TAKE
A DNA SAMPLE FROM YOU

1:14:52.237 --> 1:14:53.530
AND FROM JERRY'S CORPSE,

1:14:53.530 --> 1:14:55.699
AND WE'LL HAVE OUR ANSWER
PRETTY QUICK.

1:14:55.699 --> 1:14:57.242
I UNDERSTAND.

1:14:57.242 --> 1:15:00.162
LARRY, ARE YOU GONNA MAKE US
JUMP THROUGH ALL THESE HOOPS,

1:15:00.162 --> 1:15:02.706
PROVING WHAT'S CLEAR
TO EVERYBODY IN THIS ROOM?

1:15:02.706 --> 1:15:05.375
ALL THESE PEOPLE SAYING
GREAT THINGS ABOUT YOU --

1:15:05.375 --> 1:15:06.502
YOU WORKING HARD,

1:15:06.502 --> 1:15:08.754
KEEPING YOUR NOSE CLEAN SINCE
YOU GOT OUT.

1:15:08.754 --> 1:15:10.088
YOU'VE BEEN DOING GREAT.

1:15:10.088 --> 1:15:12.090
HOLD ONTO THAT. KEEP YOUR
DIGNITY.

1:15:12.090 --> 1:15:14.843
TELL US WHAT WENT WRONG, AND
SAVE EVERYBODY

1:15:14.843 --> 1:15:17.012
A LOT OF TIME AND A LOT
OF GRIEF.

1:15:22.100 --> 1:15:23.560
COME ON, THEN.

1:15:30.567 --> 1:15:32.903
YOU KNOW, WHEN I GOT OUT,

1:15:32.903 --> 1:15:36.406
I READ ALL OF THESE
SELF-HELP BOOKS.

1:15:36.406 --> 1:15:38.825
I WAS DETERMINED
TO MAKE IT STRAIGHT.

1:15:38.825 --> 1:15:43.038
AND THIS ONE BOOK --
IN THE LAST CHAPTER,

1:15:43.038 --> 1:15:47.209
THIS GUY...WARNS ABOUT A
FALSE EUPHORIA.

1:15:47.209 --> 1:15:50.796
YOU KNOW, AND THAT'S
WHEN YOU GET ALL CAUGHT UP

1:15:50.796 --> 1:15:53.382
IN HOW
YOU'RE IMPROVING YOURSELF

1:15:53.382 --> 1:15:55.968
AND HOW BEAUTIFUL
THE WORLD IS.

1:15:55.968 --> 1:15:59.179
AND THEN SOMETHING HAPPENS
THAT THROWS YOU

1:15:59.179 --> 1:16:02.266
BACK IN THE GUTTER --
BACK TO REALITY.

1:16:02.266 --> 1:16:06.520
I'VE BEEN WAITING FOR THAT,
BUT I THOUGHT I HAD IT LICKED.

1:16:08.814 --> 1:16:11.483
[ SIGHS ]

1:16:11.483 --> 1:16:13.277
WHAT HAPPENED THIS MORNING?

1:16:13.277 --> 1:16:14.945
I'VE BEEN OUT OF WORK,

1:16:14.945 --> 1:16:18.407
AND MY P.O.'s BEEN ON ME
TO GET A JOB.

1:16:18.407 --> 1:16:22.327
I FINALLY GOT AN INTERVIEW
FOR THIS MORNING.

1:16:22.327 --> 1:16:26.707
I GO OUT, AND MY TRUCK
HAS BEEN TOWED -- IMPOUNDED.

1:16:26.707 --> 1:16:28.625
LEFT MY WALLET IN IT.

1:16:28.625 --> 1:16:30.002
I GO TO MRS. GAVIOLA,

1:16:30.002 --> 1:16:31.920
TELL HER I NEED TO
BORROW 75 BUCKS.

1:16:31.920 --> 1:16:33.380
SHE SAYS, "NO."

1:16:33.380 --> 1:16:36.300
SHE'S HAD BAD EXPERIENCES
LOANING PEOPLE MONEY.

1:16:36.300 --> 1:16:39.052
I TELL HER I'LL BRING IT BACK
IN THREE HOURS.

1:16:39.052 --> 1:16:41.263
I NEED MY TRUCK, I NEED
MY WALLET,

1:16:41.263 --> 1:16:43.265
I NEED TO GET
TO MY INTERVIEW!

1:16:43.265 --> 1:16:45.559
I NEED TO KEEP MY HEAD
ABOVE WATER!

1:16:45.559 --> 1:16:48.895
I FOUND THIS WOMAN
ON THE FLOOR OF HER KITCHEN,

1:16:48.895 --> 1:16:51.940
'CAUSE SHE FELL OVER
TRYING TO MAKE TOAST.

1:16:51.940 --> 1:16:55.569
