WAITED ON HER FOR THREE DAYS!

1:16:55.569 --> 1:16:58.030
SO YOU SNAPPED WHEN
SHE TURNED YOU DOWN.

1:16:58.030 --> 1:16:59.114
AS SOON AS I PUT
MY HANDS ON HER,

1:16:59.114 --> 1:17:02.117
I KNEW
I WAS GOING AWAY FOREVER!

1:17:02.117 --> 1:17:03.493
IT JUST MADE ME MADDER!

1:17:03.493 --> 1:17:04.995
I HAD NOTHING AGAINST HER.

1:17:04.995 --> 1:17:07.539
I HAD NOTHING AGAINST
ANY OF THEM! I JUST...

1:17:07.539 --> 1:17:10.208
LET'S GET IT DOWN.

1:17:10.208 --> 1:17:14.796
IT'S FALSE --
ALL THE DO-GOOD CRAP.

1:17:14.796 --> 1:17:16.965
SO FALSE.

1:17:16.965 --> 1:17:20.302
IT'S ALL JUST WAITING AROUND
UNTIL THE HAMMER DROPS.

1:17:23.680 --> 1:17:26.308
IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE IN
THE PAST

1:17:26.308 --> 1:17:28.477
THAT YOU DIDN'T
GET CAUGHT FOR, LARRY?

1:17:28.477 --> 1:17:30.437
YOU WERE CONVICTED
ON ONE RAPE ASSAULT.

1:17:30.437 --> 1:17:32.230
MY GUESS IS THAT THERE WERE
OTHERS.

1:17:32.230 --> 1:17:34.149
SINCE YOU'RE COMING CLEAN --

1:17:34.149 --> 1:17:37.194
AND I THINK IT'S ADMIRABLE
THAT YOU ARE --

1:17:37.194 --> 1:17:38.737
NOW WOULD BE THE TIME

1:17:38.737 --> 1:17:41.698
TO BRING PEACE
TO OTHER PEOPLE'S FAMILIES.

1:17:41.698 --> 1:17:43.367
I CAN RESPECT THAT.

1:17:43.367 --> 1:17:45.661
WERE THERE OTHERS?

1:17:49.831 --> 1:17:53.001
THERE WAS A WAITRESS
AT THE GOLDEN LADLE DINER

1:17:53.001 --> 1:17:55.337
IN MYRTLE BEACH, SOUTH
CAROLINA.

1:17:55.337 --> 1:17:58.799
THIS WAS IN, UH, 1983.

1:17:58.799 --> 1:18:00.258
SUSIE.

1:18:00.258 --> 1:18:04.012
AND A PROSTITUTE
IN DECATUR, ILLINOIS, IN '85.

1:18:04.012 --> 1:18:07.516
HER STREET NAME WAS BUNNY.
SHE HAD RED HAIR.

1:18:10.102 --> 1:18:13.105
[ SIGHS ]

1:18:13.105 --> 1:18:15.774
YOU'RE RIGHT.

1:18:15.774 --> 1:18:18.443
I SHOULD TALK ABOUT THEM
NOW.

1:18:18.443 --> 1:18:20.779
RAPE ASSAULTS?

1:18:20.779 --> 1:18:23.115
NO, I KILLED THEM.

1:18:28.036 --> 1:18:30.497
AND THEN
YOU TOOK THE CLIP OUT?

1:18:30.497 --> 1:18:31.748
YEAH.

1:18:31.748 --> 1:18:34.793
AND YOU KEPT PLAYING
WITH THE GUN?

1:18:34.793 --> 1:18:37.087
YEAH.

1:18:37.087 --> 1:18:41.508
AND, UH, SOMEWHERE IN THERE,
YOU POINTED A GUN AT SCOTT?

1:18:41.508 --> 1:18:44.761
YEAH, WE WERE PLAYING.

1:18:44.761 --> 1:18:46.763
Junior: AND THEN YOU
PULLED THE TRIGGER?

1:18:46.763 --> 1:18:48.432
NO! I-I MEAN --

1:18:48.432 --> 1:18:50.475
WAS YOUR FINGER ON THE
TRIGGER?

1:18:50.475 --> 1:18:52.102
I HAVE A B.B. GUN,

1:18:52.102 --> 1:18:55.230
AND THAT TRIGGER --
YOU HAVE TO REALLY PULL IT.

1:18:55.230 --> 1:18:57.899
IT'S WHAT I'M USED TO.

1:18:57.899 --> 1:19:00.569
SO YOUR FINGER
JUST KIND OF SLIPPED?

1:19:00.569 --> 1:19:03.363
I-I JUST...

1:19:03.363 --> 1:19:05.532
I DON'T REMEMBER
PULLING THE TRIGGER.

1:19:05.532 --> 1:19:07.868
I DIDN'T MEAN TO IF I
DID.

1:19:07.868 --> 1:19:09.745
WERE YOU MOVING AROUND?

1:19:09.745 --> 1:19:14.708
YEAH. SCOTT WAS ACTING LIKE
HE WAS A GANGBANGER.

1:19:14.708 --> 1:19:17.669
[ Voice breaking ]
AND I WAS THE COP...

1:19:17.669 --> 1:19:20.130
A-AND HE WAS COMING AT ME.

1:19:20.130 --> 1:19:25.135
MY B.B. GUN -- I HAVE TO
REALLY PULL THE TRIGGER.

1:19:25.135 --> 1:19:28.096
AND THEN WHAT HAPPENED,
JAKE?

1:19:28.096 --> 1:19:30.348
[ WHIMPERS ]

1:19:30.348 --> 1:19:34.144
I KNOW THIS IS HARD,
BUT YOU NEED TO TELL US.

1:19:34.144 --> 1:19:38.940
THERE -- THERE WAS THIS
BIG EXPLOSION.

1:19:38.940 --> 1:19:43.111
AND -- AND THE GUN
JUMPED IN MY HAND...

1:19:43.111 --> 1:19:46.656
AND SCOTT FELL DOWN.

1:19:46.656 --> 1:19:48.742
[ SOBBING ]

1:19:48.742 --> 1:19:52.996
IT'S OKAY, SON. IT'S
OKAY.

1:19:52.996 --> 1:19:56.333
IT'S OKAY.

1:20:03.131 --> 1:20:05.133
THE SON GIVING
A STATEMENT?

1:20:05.133 --> 1:20:07.969
THE D.A.'s STILL IN THERE
WITH HIM AND THE DAD.

1:20:07.969 --> 1:20:09.262
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT?

1:20:09.262 --> 1:20:10.430
YEAH.

1:20:10.430 --> 1:20:12.265
HAS SCOTT'S MOM BEEN
NOTIFIED?

1:20:12.265 --> 1:20:14.142
I CALLED HER
TO MAKE SURE SHE WAS HOME

1:20:14.142 --> 1:20:16.019
SO WE COULD BREAK THE NEWS IN
PERSON,

1:20:16.019 --> 1:20:17.813
BUT SHE WANTED TO KNOW
ON THE PHONE.

1:20:17.813 --> 1:20:19.022
WHAT DO YOU WANNA DO

1:20:19.022 --> 1:20:21.233
ABOUT THE ASSAULT CHARGES ON THE
BOYFRIEND?

1:20:21.233 --> 1:20:22.359
WE GOT HIM DOWNSTAIRS.

1:20:22.359 --> 1:20:24.152
DROP IT. IT'S OVER
WITH.

1:20:24.152 --> 1:20:26.071
ALL RIGHT, THEN CUT
HIM LOOSE.

1:20:33.078 --> 1:20:35.038
YOU STILL COMING TONIGHT?

1:20:35.038 --> 1:20:37.415
I DIDN'T KNOW
IF WE WERE STILL ON.

1:20:37.415 --> 1:20:39.209
YEAH. SEE YOU LATER.

1:20:39.209 --> 1:20:40.252
ALL RIGHT.

1:20:45.882 --> 1:20:48.468
WHY DON'T YOU COME
AND HAVE A SEAT, MS. LOWE?

1:20:48.468 --> 1:20:50.846
YOU HAVE MY BOYFRIEND,
STEVE DANZIG, IN CUSTODY?

1:20:50.846 --> 1:20:52.430
YEAH, IT WAS A LITTLE
SCUFFLE,

1:20:52.430 --> 1:20:54.432
BUT STEVE WON'T BE CHARGED WITH
ANYTHING.

1:20:54.432 --> 1:20:55.642
WHERE IS HE?

1:20:55.642 --> 1:20:56.977
HE'S GONNA BE RELEASED.

1:20:56.977 --> 1:20:59.062
ANYTHING ELSE YOU GUYS
WANNA KNOW ABOUT ME,

1:20:59.062 --> 1:21:01.022
ANYTHING ELSE YOU WANNA
ACCUSE ME OF?

1:21:01.022 --> 1:21:03.066
WE WERE INVESTIGATING YOUR SON'S
DEATH.

1:21:03.066 --> 1:21:06.987
I LOST MY SON.
YOU MADE ME FEEL EVEN WORSE.

1:21:06.987 --> 1:21:08.864
SORRY, THAT WASN'T OUR
INTENTION.

1:21:08.864 --> 1:21:11.533
SHAME ON BOTH OF YOU.

1:21:11.533 --> 1:21:13.326
WE'RE SORRY.

1:21:13.326 --> 1:21:14.703
I WANT STEVE RELEASED RIGHT
NOW.

1:21:14.703 --> 1:21:17.163
I'LL BE OUTSIDE.

1:21:41.229 --> 1:21:44.566
SCOTT WAS KILLED ACCIDENTALLY
BY HIS FRIEND JAKE DWYER.

1:21:44.566 --> 1:21:47.068
JAKE'S DAD PANICKED AND
COVERED IT UP.

1:21:47.068 --> 1:21:49.529
I'M DROPPING THE
ASSAULT CHARGE ON YOU.

1:21:49.529 --> 1:21:51.865
YOU'RE FREE TO GO.
CATHERINE'S WAITING FOR YOU.

1:21:57.370 --> 1:21:59.831
DID YOU GO AT THEM
AS HARD AS YOU WENT AT ME?

1:21:59.831 --> 1:22:01.666
12-YEAR-OLD KID GETS KILLED,

1:22:01.666 --> 1:22:04.002
IT'S THE ONLY WAY I'M
GONNA DO IT.

1:22:04.002 --> 1:22:06.963
THEN NO HARD FEELINGS.

1:22:06.963 --> 1:22:08.673
NONE HERE EITHER.

1:22:23.813 --> 1:22:25.899
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

1:22:25.899 --> 1:22:27.233
HEY, POP.

1:22:27.233 --> 1:22:28.318
JOHN.

1:22:28.318 --> 1:22:29.861
RITA ORTIZ, THIS IS MY
DAD.

1:22:29.861 --> 1:22:31.446
JOHN CLARK. NICE TO
MEET YOU.

1:22:31.446 --> 1:22:32.906
IT'S NICE TO MEET YOU,
SIR.

1:22:38.411 --> 1:22:39.913
HEARD YOU COLLARED UP

1:22:39.913 --> 1:22:42.332
ON THAT 12-YEAR-OLD
GOT MURDERED?

1:22:42.332 --> 1:22:44.334
YEAH.

1:22:44.334 --> 1:22:47.003
THOSE ARE ALWAYS HARD.

1:22:47.003 --> 1:22:48.797
WERE YOU WORKING IT, TOO?

1:22:48.797 --> 1:22:50.298
NO, ME AND MY PARTNER CAUGHT

1:22:50.298 --> 1:22:52.634
AN ELDERLY WOMAN
MURDERED IN HER APARTMENT.

1:22:52.634 --> 1:22:54.135
IT LOOKED LIKE A GROUND BALL

1:22:54.135 --> 1:22:56.054
WITH HER JUNKIE GRANDSON
DOING IT,

1:22:56.054 --> 1:22:57.305
BUT IT TURNED OUT TO BE

1:22:57.305 --> 1:23:00.141
AN EX-CON WHO APPEARED
TO HAVE TURNED HIS LIFE AROUND.

1:23:00.141 --> 1:23:02.602
BUT HE LOST IT
AND KILLED HER THIS MORNING.

1:23:02.602 --> 1:23:04.229
HOW MUCH TIME YOU
GOT ON THE JOB?

1:23:04.229 --> 1:23:05.355
FIVE YEARS.

1:23:05.355 --> 1:23:06.773
FIVE YEARS?

1:23:06.773 --> 1:23:08.858
AND YOU'RE ALREADY
IN THE DETECTIVE BUREAU?

1:23:08.858 --> 1:23:11.611
YEAH, I GOT LUCKY.

1:23:11.611 --> 1:23:13.321
WHERE'D YOU WORK
BEFORE THIS?

1:23:13.321 --> 1:23:15.699
THREE YEARS IN THE 8-3 IN
UNIFORM,

1:23:15.699 --> 1:23:18.201
THEN TWO IN MANHATTAN SOUTH --
VICE.

1:23:18.201 --> 1:23:20.412
THIS LUCK COME IN THE FORM
OF A BIG HOOK

1:23:20.412 --> 1:23:22.580
WITH SOMEONE WHO'S GOT A LOT
OF JUICE?

1:23:22.580 --> 1:23:25.166
THEY NEEDED HISPANIC FEMALES
IN VICE.

1:23:25.166 --> 1:23:26.292
I SEE.

1:23:26.292 --> 1:23:29.629
THE BLOOMING ONION'S
BACK ON THE MENU.

1:23:29.629 --> 1:23:33.174
AM I MAKING YOU
UNCOMFORTABLE?

1:23:33.174 --> 1:23:35.135
NOT AT ALL.

1:23:35.135 --> 1:23:37.262
HMM?

1:23:37.262 --> 1:23:39.180
I GOTTA HIT THE HEAD REAL
QUICK.

1:23:41.433 --> 1:23:44.144
THROW A WARNING SHOT IF HE
LEANS ON YOU TOO HARD.

1:23:44.144 --> 1:23:45.395
I'LL BE FINE.

1:23:50.316 --> 1:23:52.819
I'VE BEEN LOOKING FORWARD TO
MEETING YOU.

1:23:52.819 --> 1:23:55.071
I KNOW HOW MUCH
JOHN LOOKS UP TO YOU.

1:23:55.071 --> 1:23:58.491
THAT'S A KIND THING
FOR YOU TO SAY.

1:23:58.491 --> 1:24:00.702
SO, THIS IS YOUR SPOT?

1:24:00.702 --> 1:24:02.662
YEAH, I BEEN COMING HERE
FOR A WHILE.

1:24:02.662 --> 1:24:05.248
I DON'T KNOW IF HE
MENTIONED IT AT ALL,

1:24:05.248 --> 1:24:07.917
BUT JOHN AND I WENT THROUGH
A ROUGH PATCH

1:24:07.917 --> 1:24:10.170
WHEN HE WENT TO WORK
AT THE 15th.

1:24:10.170 --> 1:24:12.297
WE DIDN'T TALK
FOR A WHILE.

1:24:12.297 --> 1:24:14.883
I WAS OUT OF LINE.

1:24:16.968 --> 1:24:21.431
I JUST HOPE HE KNOWS... HOW
MUCH I LOVE HIM.

1:24:23.475 --> 1:24:25.185
[ SIGHS ]

1:24:25.185 --> 1:24:27.187
I'M SURE HE KNOWS.

1:24:27.187 --> 1:24:30.273
[ CHUCKLES ]

1:24:34.611 --> 1:24:36.112
OKAY.

1:24:36.112 --> 1:24:37.489
RIDE 'EM, COWBOY.

1:24:37.489 --> 1:24:39.741
I'M GONNA STAND RIGHT
HERE.

1:24:39.741 --> 1:24:41.659
NO, I'M FINE.

1:24:41.659 --> 1:24:43.328
YOU OKAY RIDING ALONE?

1:24:43.328 --> 1:24:44.579
YEAH. LET'S GO!

1:24:44.579 --> 1:24:46.498
UH, ALL RIGHT, SWEETHEART,

1:24:46.498 --> 1:24:49.542
WE'LL BE ON THAT BENCH
RIGHT OVER THERE.

1:24:49.542 --> 1:24:51.836
OKAY.
OKAY.

1:24:51.836 --> 1:24:54.047
HAVE FUN.

1:25:00.720 --> 1:25:03.181
THEO REALLY TAKES YOU
AWAY FROM IT.

1:25:03.181 --> 1:25:05.600
YEAH.

1:25:05.600 --> 1:25:08.186
OH, IS IT TOO LATE
TO GET HIM A COTTON CANDY?

1:25:08.186 --> 1:25:10.563
STAY HERE A SEC.

1:25:14.067 --> 1:25:16.778
UH, LOOK, IF ANYTHING
HAPPENS TO ME,

1:25:16.778 --> 1:25:19.197
I WANT YOU TO TAKE
CARE OF THEO.

1:25:21.116 --> 1:25:23.034
I MEAN, I'D WANT IT LEGAL.

1:25:23.034 --> 1:25:26.287
IT WOULDN'T BE A
FINANCIAL BURDEN ON YOU.

1:25:26.287 --> 1:25:29.874
THAT'S ALL SQUARED AWAY,
IF YOU'RE UP FOR THAT.

1:25:29.874 --> 1:25:32.585
OF COURSE I AM.

1:25:40.927 --> 1:25:43.429
THEO ASKED IF HE COULD
CALL YOU MOM.

1:25:43.429 --> 1:25:45.849
DO<i> YOU </i>WANT HIM TO CALL ME MOM?

1:25:45.849 --> 1:25:48.601
I DON'T WANT TO
DISRESPECT HIS MOTHER.

1:25:48.601 --> 1:25:51.437
WELL, I DON'T THINK IT'S
DISRESPECTFUL.

1:25:51.437 --> 1:25:53.690
I THINK
HIS MOTHER WOULD WANT

1:25:53.690 --> 1:25:56.651
SOMEONE IN THEO'S LIFE HE COULD
CALL MOM.

1:25:56.651 --> 1:26:02.365
SOMEONE IN<i> BOTH </i>YOUR LIVES.

1:26:02.365 --> 1:26:04.993
YEAH, YOU'RE PROBABLY RIGHT.

1:26:15.295 --> 1:26:17.547
THAT WASN'T SO BAD, WAS
IT?

1:26:20.216 --> 1:26:22.302
NO.

1:26:22.302 --> 1:26:24.429
NOT BAD AT ALL.

1:26:32.812 --> 1:26:35.023
TOMORROW NIGHT,
WE'RE GETTING A SITTER,

1:26:35.023 --> 1:26:37.734
AND YOU'RE COMING OVER
TO MY APARTMENT FOR DINNER.

1:26:37.734 --> 1:26:39.527
SOUNDS GOOD.

1:26:39.527 --> 1:26:41.196
[ FOOTSTEPS ]

1:26:41.196 --> 1:26:42.697
HEY, YOU HAVE FUN?

1:26:42.697 --> 1:26:46.284
YEAH! CAN I HAVE SOME
COTTON CANDY, PLEASE?

1:26:46.284 --> 1:26:47.869
YEAH, ALL RIGHT.

